Commentary: Shoriful Islam begins with a length ball, angling in, down the leg side. Oshada Fernando looks to flick but he misses.
Back of a length, around off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out.
Angling in, fuller ball, around the pads. Oshada Fernando flicks it past mid-wicket for a brace. Oshada Fernando and Sri Lanka are underway!
Shorter ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Good-length delivery, outside off, shaping away. Oshada Fernando leaves it alone.
On a length, swinging away, outside off. Oshada Fernando presses forward and blocks it out solidly.
Khaled Ahmed starts off with a length delivery from over the wicket, shaping away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne shoulders his arms at it.
Shorter this time, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne punches it off the back foot towards cover-point for a single. He gets off the mark!
Back of a length, around off. Oshada Fernando covers the line and defends it out.
FOUR! Top shot! Shorter ball again, outside off. Oshada Fernando gets on top of teh bounce, opens the face of the bat, and guides it past backward point for a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Marginally short, width on offer this time. Oshada Fernando hangs back and slashes it past point for another boundary.
Touch fuller, outside off. Oshada Fernando lunges forward and defends it out. Good over for Sri Lanka! 9 runs off it.
Tailing back in, on a length, around the leg pole. Dimuth Karunaratne gets inside the line and flicks it past mid-wicket. Two taken!
Another one angling in, much fuller on this occasion, around his pads. Dimuth Karunaratne clips it and finds the fielder at mid-wicket.
Pitches it up, on the pads. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it through square leg. Single taken!
Fuller in length again, around off. Oshada Fernando miscues his drive towards mid off.
Back of a length, outside off. Oshada Fernando taps it towards point off the back foot.
Full in length, outside off. Oshada Fernando shows the full face of the bat and drives it towards the fielder at mid off.
Good-length delivery, outside off, this one stays low as well. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it towards extra cover.
Swing and a miss! Marginally short, angling away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to pull this but he fails to get any connection on it.
Another play and a miss! Back of a length, shaping away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne tries to cut this away but he gets beaten.
Length delivery, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it wide of mid on and gets off strike.

Much better from Khaled Ahmed! Touch fuller, angling into the right-hander, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando looks to flick this but the ball goes off the inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Fuller, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out solidly.

A huge shout for LBW, but the umpire says no! A length ball, angling shaping away a tad, around middle. Oshada Fernando looks to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his pads. Bangladesh opts for a review! The replay rolls in. No bat involved confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracking indicates the ball was pitching outside leg. Bangladesh loses a review.
Angling away, fuller ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out.
Full in length, outside off. Oshada Fernando presses forward and defends it out.
Shoriful Islam digs it short now, outside off, angling away. Oshada Fernando sways away from it.
Swinging away, on a length, outside off. Oshada Fernando lets that go through to the keeper.
BEATEN! Well bowled! Tight length from Oshada Fernando now, shaping away outside off. Oshada Fernando looks to block this but he gets beaten as the ball zips past his outside edge.
Angling across, on a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it towards cover off the back foot and rotates the strike.
Fuller delivery, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando blocks it towards mid on.

Khaled Ahmed pitches it up now, around middle. Oshada Fernando pushes it towards the right of the bowler. Oshada Fernando stretches his right hand out and tries to catch it but he misses and the ball deflects off his fingers and goes towards mid on. No run taken there!
No ball! Shortish ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando defends it out solidly off the back foot. Oshada Fernando has overstepped here and a no ball is called!
Back of a length, outside off. Oshada Fernando pushes it back to the bowler.

Good fielding! Khaled Ahmed hits the deck hard, and serves a shorter ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando reaches out to it and pulls it towards mid-wicket. Nayeem Hasan there dives to his right and makes a good stop.
On a length, around middle. Oshada Fernando presents the full face of the bat and blocks it out.
Length, around middle and off. Dimuth Karunaratne taps it off the back foot towards cover-point and scampers across for a single.
Shortish ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando stands tall, gets on top of the bounce, and punches it solidly towards the fielder at cover.
Another short ball, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando pulls it gently towards deep square leg for a single.
Beaten! On a length, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne leans forward and tries to block it but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fuller this time, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it past cover. The ball will not race away towards the boundary but the batters pick up two runs.
Angling in, around middle and leg, fuller in length. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it towards mid on.
Nayeem Hasan begins with a fuller ball, tosses it up, around off. Oshada Fernando pushes it back to the bowler.
Loopy delivery, slower through the air, full, around middle. Oshada Fernando pushes it towards the right of the bowler this time.
Flighted delivery, very full, around off. Oshada Fernando steps down the wicket and tries to flick this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards deep point.
Fuller ball, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.

OUT! LBW! Nayeem Hasan comes into the attack and he strikes! He gets rid of the Sri Lankan skipper, Dimuth Karunaratne! Good move to get the spinner on. He has made early inroads here for Bangladesh. A shorter ball, coming in with the angle, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne makes room and tries to cut this away, but the ball goes on to hit the top of his back pad. A loud shout for LBW and the umpire raises his finger! Dimuth Karunaratne decides to take it upstairs. The replay rolls in and it confirms that the ball hits the pads first. Ball Tracking indicates it is the umpire's call on the impact and Dimuth Karunaratne walks back.
Fuller ball, outside off. Kusal Mendis presses forward and blocks it out solidly. End of a successful first over from Nayeem Hasan!
Length ball, angling in, outside off. Oshada Fernando leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, outside off, this one holds its line. Oshada Fernando offers no shot to that.
Fuller this time, tailing back in, around off. Oshada Fernando drives it towards extra cover. Mushfiqur Rahim does well there to stop the ball.
Tad short this time, around middle and off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out watchfully.

Yorker-length delivery, outside off. Oshada Fernando squeezes it out towards cover-point and scampers across the end. The fielder there fails to pick up the ball cleanly and the batters complete the run comfortably.
Fuller ball, angling in, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis tucks it with the inner half of his bat towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up delivery, very full, around the leg pole. Oshada Fernando flicks it towards short fine leg.
Tad shorter, around middle. Oshada Fernando blocks it out.

SIX! Up and over! Good use of his feet! A fuller ball, tad quicker, around middle. Oshada Fernando shimmies down the pitch and lofts it straight down the ground. The ball hits the boundary cushions directly and it's a maximum!
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, full, on middle. Kusal Mendis defends it out.
Shorter ball, spinning away a tad, around off. Kusal Mendis pushes it past cover off the back for a brace.
Fuller ball from over the wicket, outside off. Oshada Fernando defends it out towards point.
On a length, outside off. Oshada Fernando defends it towards cover.
Beaten! Length ball, outside off, shaping away a tad. Oshada Fernando stays back and tries to cut this away but he gets beaten.
Fuller, angling in, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando flicks it towards mid-wicket.
On a length, around middle. Oshada Fernando presents the full face of the bat and pushes it towards mid on.
Back of a length, outside off. Oshada Fernando blocks it out towards cover.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around middle. Kusal Mendis presses forward and defends it out solidly.
Very full again, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis defends it out off the front foot.
Outside off, loopy ball, full in length. Kusal Mendis lunges forward and defends it out.
Fuller in length, around middle and leg, slower through the air. Kusal Mendis defends it out.
Spinning in, full, around middle and off. Kusal Mendis is solid in his front defense.
Tad shorter, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis flicks it off the back foot towards square leg.
Length, outside off. Oshada Fernando pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Oshada Fernando chops it towards the fielder at backward point.
Length ball, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando defends it out.
Good shot! On a length, around off. Oshada Fernando opens the face of the bat and guides it past the diving fielder at cover-point. Two taken!
Length delivery, around middle. Oshada Fernando pushes it to mid on.
Tad fuller, around middle. Oshada Fernando shows the full face of the bat and pushes it right of the fielder at mid on.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Short this time, around off. Kusal Mendis rocks back and cuts it past cover-point for a boundary.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle and off. Kusal Mendis defends it out off the front foot.
Pitches it up, around off. Kusal Mendis pushes it back to the bowler.
Tosses it up, slower through the air, full, around off. Kusal Mendis presses forward and defends it out.
Tad shorter now, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis tucks it towards fine leg for a couple of runs.
Spinning in around middle, tad quciker. Kusal Mendis defends it out off the back foot.
Beaten! Outside off, shaping away, on a length. Oshada Fernando hangs back and tries to cut this away but he misses.
Fullish ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando gets forward and blocks it out.
Overpitched delivery, outside off. Oshada Fernando drives it through point. Single taken!
Fuller delivery, on middle. Kusal Mendis blocks it out solidly.

Good change of length from Khaled Ahmed! He digs it short this time, around middle and off. Kusal Mendis tries to pull but the ball goes off the top edge just over the fielder at square leg. The batters take two runs.
Fuller ball, outside off. Kusal Mendis drives it firmly towards the fielder at mid off.
Tosses it up, slower through the air, fuller ball, around middle. Oshada Fernando knocks it down to mid on for a single.
Floated delivery, full, outside off. Kusal Mendis has defended this off the front foot.
Shortish ball, around off. Kusal Mendis rocks back, opens the face of the bat and steers it past point for a brace.
Fuller ball, loopy delivery, outside off. Kusal Mendis lunges forward and defends it out.
Turning in, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis turns this to square leg.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around off. Kusal Mendis defends it out.
Fuller ball, around middle. Oshada Fernando gets down on his knee and tries to scoop this but the ball goes off his glove towards short fine leg.
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Oshada Fernando defends it out.
Spinning away, outside off, fuller ball. Oshada Fernando taps it wide of first slip.
Tosses it up, full in length, spinning away. Oshada Fernando presses forward and defends it out.
Flighted delivery, fuller ball, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando blocks it towards the leg side.
Tossed up, full, around middle. Oshada Fernando blocks it out. A maiden over from Taijul Islam!
Slower through the air, full, around middle. Kusal Mendis steps down and pushes it right of the bowler.
Fuller ball, around off. Kusal Mendis defends it out.
Shorter ball, spinning in, around off. Kusal Mendis pushes it past cover off the back foot for a single.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando rocks back and tries to flick this but he misses and gets hit on his pads.
Fuller ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando defends it out.
Floated delivery, fuller ball, around off. Oshada Fernando steps down the wicket and pushes it towards mid off.
Slower through the air, fuller delivery, around off. Kusal Mendis drives it towards mid off.
Tosses it up, full outside off. Kusal Mendis defends it out.
Spinning away a tad, full again, around off. Kusal Mendis blocks it out off the front foot.
Tossed up delivery, outside off. Kusal Mendis drives this towards cover.
Fuller ball, loopy delivery, outside off. Kusal Mendis blocks it out.
Shorter ball now, outside off. Kusal Mendis hangs back and pushes it through cover-point for a brace.
FOUR! Perfect execution! Oshada Fernando is looking well settled now! Fuller ball, around off and middle. Oshada Fernando gets down on his knee and reverse-sweeps this past point for a boundary.
Fuller ball, outside off, loopy delivery. Oshada Fernando strokes through cover for a single.
Spinning in, outside off, shorter ball. Kusal Mendis pushes it off the back foot towards deep point for a single.
Good running! Fuller ball, flighted delivery, outside off. Oshada Fernando drives it through cover for a brace.
Tossed it up, full in length, outside off. Oshada Fernando looks to drive this but the ball goes off the inner half of his bat back to the bowler.
Tossed up delivery, outside off, fuller ball. Oshada Fernando manages to get a  leading edge towards cover.
Quicker through the air, fuller, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis miscues his sweep shot towards square leg for a single.
Quick again, fullish ball, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando pushes it back to the bowler.
Tosses it up, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando presses forward, shows the full face of the bat, and defends it out.
Shortish ball, outside off. Oshada Fernando hangs back, opens the face of his bat and dabs it past point for a brace.
Much flatter this time, around middle and leg. Oshada Fernando flicks it wide of mid on Two taken!
Loopy delivery, full in length, around middle. Oshada Fernando presses forward and blocks it out watchfully.
Good shot! Shorter ball, around off. Kusal Mendis uses the depth of his crease and pushes it in the gap between mid off and extra over. Three taken!

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Bangladesh have broken this partnership! It's Nayeem Hasan who strikes once again. Much-needed wicket this, they have got rid of a well-settled batter. A loopy ball, fuller, outside off, straighter ball. Oshada Fernando leans forward and tries to block this but he gets a slight outside edge back to the keeper. Litton Das grabs it safely. An appeal for caught behind and the umpire raises his finger! Oshada Fernando takes a review immediately. UltraEdge does show a spike as the ball passes through the bat. Sri Lanka loses a review and Angelo Mathews has to walk back.
Howout: c Litton Das b Nayeem Hasan

Commentary: Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews flicks it past the short leg fielder.
Fuller in length, loopy ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews lunges forward and defends it out.
Fuller again, outside off stump. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Quicker this time, full in length, around middle. Angelo Mathews watchfully blocks it out.
A length ball, angling in, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis tucks it through mid-wicket for a single.

A length ball, nipping in, around middle and off. Angelo Mathews looks to flick but he misses and gets rapped on his pads. An appeal for LBW, and the umpire says no! Mominul Haque opts for a review! Nothing on UltraEdge. Ball Tracking indicates the impact was outside off. Bangladesh have lost their second review already!
Fuller ball, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews let's go through to the keeper.
On a length, around off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Much fuller this time, around off. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards the fielder at mid on.
Tosses it up, slower through the air, full, outside off. Kusal Mendis leans and drives it past cover for a brace.
Shortish ball, outside off. Kusal Mendis rocks and steers it down to third man. Two taken!
A similar delivery and a similar shot as well! Outside off, shortish ball. Kusal Mendis rocks back and chops it towards third man for another two.
Shorter ball, spinning in, down leg. Kusal Mendis pulls this square on the leg side. Litton Das moves across to the leg side and gets hit on his helmet. The physio is out there!
Marginally short again, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis tucks it towards fine leg.
Quicker, full, around middle. Kusal Mendis defends it from within the crease. That will be Lunch on Day 1!
Begins well after the break! On a length and around off, blocked.
On middle, Angelo works it towards mid-wicket for one. First run of the session.
A single for Mendis now! Shorter and on off, Mendis pushes it towards cover for one.
A short one, good change in length. Mathews does struggle against the bumper but this time he ducks under it nicely.
Fuller and on middle, Mathews drives it firmly towards mid on. The fielder makes a half stop. A single results.
An effort ball to end! Bangs it short but outside off. Evaded.
Tossed up delivery angling in, Angelo Mathews blocks it away.
Slower one on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes it back towards the bowler.
Fuller one on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Tossed up delivery on middle, this is defended towards the covers.
SIX! Tossed up delivery, Angelo Mathews comes forward and hits it over long on and into the stands. This was effortless.
Tossed up on middle, this is defended.
FOUR! Shorter one outside off, Kusal Mendis drives it through covers for a boundary.
On a length swinging it in, this is pushed towards mid off region.
Shorter one on middle, Kusal Mendis hits it hard towards square leg.
Shorter one on middle, Kusal Mendis ducks under it. The ball goes towards the keeper.
On a length outside off, Kusal Mendis lets it through to the keeper.
Back of the length angling in, this is blocked solidly.
Flighted one on off, this is pushed towards cover.
Fuller one on off, Angelo Mathews defends it towards mid on.
Quicker one on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Back of the length and on middle, Angelo Mathews goes on the back foot and defends it. This is a maiden over.
Fuller one on off, this is played towards covers for one.
Fuller one angling in, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards square leg.
On a length outside off, Angelo Mathews eases it towards point.
Shorter one swinging it in, Angelo Mathews plays it towards the mid-wicket region.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards mid-wicket for one.
On off, this is defended.
Tossed up on leg, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards backward square leg for one.
Tossed up on leg, Kusal Mendis just gets a bat on it as the ball goes towards backward square leg for one.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews almost gets beaten there but manages to gets his bat on it.
FOUR! Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews sweeps it through square leg for a boundary. This is a very productive shot from Angelo Mathews.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews plays it towards the third man region and rotates the strike.
FOUR! Fuller one on middle, this is a poor delivery. Kusal Mendis gets on his knees and smashes it through square leg for a boundary.
Back of the length and on middle, Angelo Mathews pulls it through the mid-wicket region. Lots of time for the batter. 3 runs taken.
Fuller one on middle, this is driven towards covers.
Good length outside off, this is driven towards covers for a couple.
FOUR BYES! Shorter one on leg, Kusal Mendis ducks under it and it beats the keeper as well. This was a poor delivery which costs the team a boundary.
Back of the length and on middle, Kusal Mendis plays it towards point.
On a length outside off, this is driven through covers for two.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards backward square leg and gets a couple.
Fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews intentionally gets an outside edge as the ball goes towards the third man region. Couple taken.
Fuller one and on middle, Angelo Mathews comes forward and pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
Fuller one and on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and plays it towards covers for one.
On a length and on middle, Kusal Mendis pushes it towards mid off for one.
Fuller one outside off, Kusal Mendis cuts it towards point for one.
On a length and on off, this is driven towards covers for a single.
Fuller one on middle, this is defended towards covers.
On a length and on middle, this is played towards mid off for one.
Tossed up delivery on leg, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
Fuller one on middle, Kusal Mendis pulls it towards square leg for one.
FOUR! On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews drives it through covers for a boundary. A much needed one for the team.
Shorter one outside off, this is swept this time for one.
Fuller one this time, this is flicked through mid-wicket.
On a length and on middle, Kusal Mendis works it towards backward square leg for one.
Fuller one this time, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and blocks it out.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Kusal Mendis eases it towards covers.
Fuller one on off, Kusal Mendis defends it towards covers.
On a length and on middle, this is defended towards silly mid-off.
Fuller one on middle, this is played towards covers.
Tossed up delivery on middle, this is played towards covers. A quick single taken.
Fuller one on off, Angelo Mathews moves to his backfoot and punches it towards mid off for one.
Shakib Al Hasan begins with a shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Angelo Mathews pushes it off the back foot towards cover. A little fumble by the fielder there allows them to take a single.
Fuller this time, around middle. Kusal Mendis blocks it out.
Shorter ball, outside off. Kusal Mendis punches it off the back foot towards extra cover.
Pitches it up, around middle and leg. Kusal Mendis flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around off. Kusal Mendis presses forward and blocks it out solidly.
Loopy delivery, around off, fuller ball. Kusal Mendis defends it out. 1 run off Shakib Al Hasan's first over!
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid on.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
FOUR! Fuller one on off, Angelo Mathews drives it through covers for a boundary. This is an excellent shot.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
Fuller one on middle, This is played towards the mid-wicket region.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Kusal Mendis pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Kusal Mendis defends it solidly.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Kusal Mendis flicks it towards mid-wicket region.
Fuller one on leg, Kusal Mendis defends it solidly.
Fuller one on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Fuller one on off, this is played towards backward point.
Flatter and on middle, defended.
Well played in the end! This is flatter, it lands and then skids through. Angelo goes back to block but gets his bat down in time.
Fires this one on middle, Mathews blocks it out.
Slows it up, lands it on off. Angelo Mathews lunges and plays it out.
A little too straight, this is clipped through square leg for one.
A dot to end! Tossed up on off, Mendis pushes it to covers.
Flatter and on off, this is pushed to covers.
On middle, kept out.
Could have been a chance had he picked it up cleanly! On off, this is pushed towards cover. The batters take off. The fielder gets to the ball but fails to pick it up. The single is easy in the end.
Well bowled! This is angled into middle, it goes on with the angle. Mendis defends outside the line, it goes off the inner half through square leg for one.
Floats it up on off, blocked.
A little too full, Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Fires this one on off, Mendis guides it to point.
Tosses it up a little and lands it on off, Mendis plays it to covers.
Slightly shorter but quicker, on off, Mendis guides it to point.
Make that 4 dots in a row! On off, Mendis hangs back and plays it to point again.
5 dots in a row now! On off, it is kept out. Can he bowl a maiden?
Yes, he does! Another one darted on the off pole, Mendis plays it to covers. The two spinners have put a halt on the run-flow.
Gives it air, lands it on off, Angelo Mathews plays it to covers. Good tidy stuff.
Gets away with one! This is shorter and outside off, Angelo Mathews hangs back and cuts but to point.
Slower through the air and on middle, kept out.
Another one tossed up nicely on middle, Angelo Mathews gets behind the line and defends.
5 dots in this over as well! On middle, this is worked to mid-wicket. Can there be back-to-back maidens?
Make that two maidens in a row! On middle, Mathews plays it onto the ground.
On middle, kept out.

The series of dots have ended as Mendis goes back and pushes this through covers for one. Also, that is fifty for Mendis. A classy innings from him and a welcome one for Lanka. He needs to go on now, there is a big one on the offer.
Attacks the stumps, blocked.
The series of dots continue for Angelo Mathews! On the stumps, he is solid in defense.
It ends for him too as he works this with the angle through mid-wicket for one.
Shorter and outside off, this is pushed through covers for one.
Tossed up on off, blocked.
Gives it air, lands it on off, Mendis plays it to covers.
Flighted delivery, on off, no turn for Shakib. Easily negotiated.
Continues to attack the stumps, Mendis is up for the task as he pushes it to covers.
Very good from Shakib! Giving nothing to the batter, making him play every ball by attacking the stumps. Mendis is happy to block it out.
On a length and on middle, Kusal Mendis plays it towards mid-wicket for one.
Flatter and on off, Mathews blocks it out.
On off, Mathews pushes it to covers.

NOT OUT! No spike on Ultra Edge and the on-field call has to be overturned! Excellent use of the review by Mathews. There was some sound though but maybe it was of the bat hitting the pad. This is tossed up on off, this lands and then spins away. Mathews looks to defend but it seems like the ball has taken the edge. Das takes it and appeals, the finger goes up. Mathews has a puzzled look on his face, he reviews after a chat with his partner. There is a spike on Ultra Edge but that is before the ball passes the bat. It is probably then when Mathews hits his pad with the bat. There is no spike as the ball passes close to the bat. Angelo survives.
On middle, defended.
Flighted and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes it to covers.
On the stumps, kept out.
On off, this is pushed to the bowler.
Flatter and on middle, defended.
Slows it up and lands it on off, Mendies pushes it to covers.
Floats it up on off, Mendis pushes it to covers.
Very full and on off, Mendis strokes it to the bowler.
Angled into middle, Mendis works it to mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle and off. Angelo Mathews defends it out.

Turn and bounce this time! A shorter ball, spinning away, around off. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards cover. He leaves his crease for a single, but he decides against it at the end. Good call from him!
Loopy delivery, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews tucks it through square leg for a single.
Floated delivery, full in length, around off. Kusal Mendis has blocked this off the front foot.
Marginally short, around middle. Kusal Mendis defends it out off the back foot.
Tosses it up, around middle. Kusal Mendis defends it out watchfully. Just one run off the over.
From over the wicket now, this is flatter and on off, it is pushed through covers for one.
Flatter and on off, Mendis pushes it to covers.
Loopy ball on middle, Mendis keeps it out.
Another flighted delivery and on off, this is pushed to covers.
Quicker and on off, Mendis pushes it to covers.
Angled into middle, Mendis plays it to the man at covers.

Flatter again and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes it through covers and gets to the other end.

On middle, defended.
Another one on the stumps, played easily on the off side.
Fires it on middle, kept out.
Floats it up, this is angled into middle, Angelo Mathews was probably looking to play it off the back foot but then realises it is too full to do so. He gets his bat down in time and keeps it out.
Gives it air and lands it on middle, blocked.
Fuller and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes it to covers.

Floats it up on off, kept out.

Shorter and on off, Mendis pushes it to covers.

Yet another maiden! Outside off, left alone. Some turn for Taijul Islam!
Angled into middle, Angelo Mathews works it to mid-wicket.
That was the sucker ball! Slows it up, bowls it full and wide outside off. Mathews though shoulders arms to it.
Now pushes it through, on off, Mathews goes back and cuts it to point.
A little bit of turn! This lands on off and then straightens. Mathews was thinking of pulling it but then defends.
A single now! Tossed up on off, this is pushed down to long off for one.
On middle, kept out.
Another dot! On off, it is played back to the bowler.
Angled into middle, Angelo Mathews plays it out.
Slower through the air and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes it to covers.
This one angles into the middle pole, Mathews shows the full face of the bat and plays it to covers.
On the stumps, blocked.
Slower through the air and on off, Mathews pushes it to covers.
Fuller one on middle, Kusal Mendis plays it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up on middle, this is played towards square leg for one.
On a length outside off, Kusal Mendis dabs it towards point and rotates the strike.
On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews hits it hard towards square leg.
Tossed up delivery one middle, Kusal Mendis blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Kusal Mendis goes on his backfoot nd punches it towards mid off.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
On the pads, Fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews tries to play it as it hits his pads.
On a length outside off, Angelo Mathews plays it towards covers.
On a length and on off, this is pushed back towards covers.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews uses hits feet and smashes it towards long off and gets a single.
Tossed up delivery on middle, this is defended towards covers.
FOUR! A fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and hits it hard towards mid-wicket. The fielder chases it but can only escort the ball to the boundary line.
On a length and on middle, this is played towards square leg for one. 50 up for Angelo Mathews.
Back of the length and outside off, Kusal Mendis cuts it through point and rotates the strike.
On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes the ball back towards Khaled Ahmed.
Fuller one outside off, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid on region.
FOUR! An excellent shot by Angelo Mathews. Fuller one outside off, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and flicks it through mid-wicket. The ball goes behind the ropes for a boundary.

OUT! TAKEN! What a start for Bangladesh! A wicket on the very first delivery after Tea. A perfect start for them and the partnership has finally been broken. Not best of deliveries by Taijul Islam but he gets away with it. A shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Kusal Mendis looks to pull but he ends up dragging it with the inner half of his bat towards mid-wicket. Nayeem Hasan there pouches it safely. Kusal Mendis departs after a well-made 54!
Howout: c Nayeem Hasan b Taijul Islam

Commentary: Shortish ball, an arm ball, around middle. Dhananjaya de Silva tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller length delivery, around off, loopy ball. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.
Marginally short, around middle and off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, spinning away, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva presses forward and dabs it towards point.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Dhananjaya de Silva knocks it towards mid-wicket.

EDGED AND AWAY! FOUR! A fuller ball, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews looks to flick this but he gets an inside edge, towards the keeper. Litton Das dives to his left, but he fails to reach the ball. It races away towards fine leg for a boundary.
Angling in, around middle and leg, on a length. Angelo Mathews works it away towards mid-wicket.
Another length delivery, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews works it away towards square leg for a single.
Much fuller this time, tailing back in, on the pads. Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it through square leg. Single taken!
Khaled Ahmed pitches it up again, on the pads. Angelo Mathews works it away towards deep square leg and rotates the strike.
Full in length, outside off, at 128.9 clicks. Dhananjaya de Silva presses forward and defends it towards cover.
Shortish ball, spinning away, around middle. Angelo Mathews rocks back and defends it out.
Tosses it up now, fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews lunges forward and blocks it out.
Outside off, full again. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards extra cover.
Loopy delivery, around middle. Angelo Mathews has defended this solidly off the front foot.
Flighted delivery, outside off. Angelo Mathews blocks it towards the off side.
Fullish again, quicker through the air, around off. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Width on offer, shorter ball. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it off the back foot towards the fielder at cover-point.
Pitched up, around middle and leg. Dhananjaya de Silva works it away towards mid-wicket.
Darting it on the pads, fuller in length. Dhananjaya de Silva tucks it towards deep square leg. Easy runs for the batter here!
On a length, outside off. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards mid off.
Back of a length, outside off, at around 132 clicks. Angelo Mathews punches it off the back foot towards the fielder at mid off. Tidy over from Khaled Ahmed. 1 run off it.
Well left! Some turn there! A fuller ball, outside off, spinning away. Dhananjaya de Silva lunges and leaves it alone.
Fuller ball, around middle, much quicker this time. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it out.
An arm ball! This one comes in with the angle, around middle and leg. Dhananjaya de Silva looks to flick but he misses and gets hit on the pads. A stifled appeal for LBW, but the umpire is unmoved.
Tosses it up, much quicker on this occasion, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it towards point for a single. Good change of pace from Taijul Islam!
Loopy delivery, full, outside the off pole. Angelo Mathews drives it powerfully through cover. The ball will not race away but the batters get two runs.
Outside off, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews defends it towards point off the front foot.
Length is a tad fuller on this occasion, outside off. Dhananjaya de Silva defends it towards cover.
Pitches it up again, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out.
Angling in, on a length, around off. Dhananjaya de Silva pushes it towards mid off from within the crease.
On a length, angling it into the pads, at 126.5 clicks. Dhananjaya de Silva works it away towards square leg for a single.
Shoriful Islam drops it short this time, around middle, at around 131 clicks. Angelo Mathews ducks underneath it.
Another back-of-a-length delivery, around middle. Angelo Mathews miscues his pull shot towards deep square leg for a single.
Tossed up delivery, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and plays it towards mid off for one.
Fuller one on middle, Dhananjaya de Silva pushes the ball back towards the bowler.
Fuller one outside off, Dhananjaya de Silva cuts it towards point.
Tossed up delivery, Dhananjaya de Silva defends it solidly.
Yorker one middle, Dhananjaya de Silva blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Dhananjaya de Silva tries to loft but it hits the upper part of the bat. The ball was in the air for some time but no fielder there. He gets lucky this time.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews drives it towards mid-wicket region.
Back of the length and on off, Angelo Mathews defends the ball back towards the bowler.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes the ball towards the mid-wicket region.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews flicks the ball towards square leg for one.
On a length outside off, Dhananjaya de Silva leaves it.
Back of the length and on middle, Dhananjaya de Silva defends the ball back towards the bowler.
On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews defends the ball solidly.
FOUR! On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and flicks the ball through mid-wicket. The ball goes behind the ropes for a boundary.

FOUR! A chance there for a catch. Angelo Mathews gets lucky. A fuller one outside off, Angelo Mathews tries to defend it but gets an outside edge. The fielder on the slip dives to his left but couldn't catch it. The ball rolls over the boundary line.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews plays it towards mid on region.
A slower one on off, Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews defends the ball back towards the bowler.
Fuller one on off, Dhananjaya de Silva flicks it over mid-wicket and gets a couple.

OUT! CAUGHT! Shakib Al Hasan comes into the attack and strikes straightaway! Dhananjaya de Silva departs for a timid score. Tossed up delivery, on middle, this one comes in with the angle. Dhananjaya de Silva tries to defend it but the ball hits his pads and lobs up towards first slip. Mahmudul Hasan Joy there runs forward, dives and pouches it safely. Bangladesh players think he has got an inside edge and they appeal for a catch! The umpire says no! Mominul Haque opts for a review! UltraEdge shows a spike as the ball passes through the bat. Finally, a successful review for Bangladesh and they have got their fourth wicket.
Howout: c Mahmudul Hasan Joy b Shakib Al Hasan

Commentary: Tossed up delivery on middle, Dinesh Chandimal eases it towards mid-wicket region.
Fuller one outside off, Dinesh Chandimal defends it solidly.

Just short! Mathews played that with soft hands. On off, this lands and turns away. Mathews looks to defend, this goes off the outside edge but lands well short of the first slip fielder.

Fuller one on middle, Dinesh Chandimal bumps the ball as the ball goes towards covers where the fielder catches it. A loud appeal by the team. Third umpire shows that the ball bumps on the ground before the catch was taken. Not out.
Fuller one on off, Dinesh Chandimal eases it towards mid on region.
FOUR! Fuller one outside off, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and lofts it over mid on. The ball goes behind the ropes for a one bounce boundary.

FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! This is good batting from Angelo Mathews! Fuller one on off, Angelo Mathews tonks it over long off this time. The ball goes one bounce over the ropes for another boundary.
Goes wide outside off, Angelo Mathews drives it towards covers.
Goes fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes it back towards the bowler.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.

SIX! Fuller and on middle, Dinesh Chandimal lofts it over long on for a biggie. This is a brilliant shot.

Tossed up on off, this is pushed to cover again.

Flatter on middle, Dinesh Chandimal pushes it towards mid off, he wanted one but is sent back.

Chandimal comes down the track but the length is shortened, it is pushed to cover.

On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards square leg.

On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.

On the stumps, defended.

Tossed up delivery on middle, Angelo Mathews eases it towards covers.

Fuller one and on middle, Dinesh Chandimal hits it towards mid off region. He wanted a single but Angelo Mathews sends him back.
On a length on middle, Dinesh Chandimal goes on his backfoot and flicks it towards mid on region.
FOUR! Good shot! Tosses it up, full and outside off. Angelo Mathews lunges and drives it through extra cover for a boundary. He moves on to 92!
Loopy delivery, full, around middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Very full again, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards the fielder at mid-wicket.
Darting it down the leg side, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews tickles it fine towards fine leg for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle, slower through the air. Dinesh Chandimal works it away towards mid on.
Loopy ball, pitched up, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal steps down the wicket and pushes it back to the bowler.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg, much straighter on this occasion. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards deep square leg for a single.
SIX! BANG! Wonderful shot! Outside off, fuller ball, slower through the air. Dinesh Chandimal dances down the wickets and smashes it over long off for a biggie.
Shorter now, around middle and off. Dinesh Chandimal cuts it towards cover.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal stays back and pushes it towards cover.
Fuller ball, drifting in, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Quicker, full, around off. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out.
Outside off, full in length. Angelo Mathews steps down the pitch and drives it firmly towards the fielder at cover.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews flicks it towards long on for a single.
Loopy delivery, fuller ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.
Fuller ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal steps down and pushes it towards long on for a single.
Shorter ball, drifting down the leg side. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards fine leg for a single.
Back of a length, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal cuts it wide of slip for a single.
Shorter ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal taps it towards point.
A length ball, down the leg side. Dinesh Chandimal looks to flick but he misses.
On a length, darting it on the pads. Dinesh Chandimal clips it towards deep square leg for three runs.

FOUR! Angelo Mathews brings up his century in style! A fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews uses his wrists and flicks it past mid-wicket for a boundary. His 12th Test match century. He removes his helmet and lifts his bat high. What a knock this has been!
Outside off, on a length. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Another length delivery, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, quicker, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal clips it towards square leg and rotates the strike.
Fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews nudges it towards square leg for a single.
Tosses it up now, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal works it away towards square leg for a single.
Outside off, slower through the air, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Very full, tossed it up, around middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it down the long on for a single.
Shorter this time, around middle and leg. Angelo nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Outside off, on a length. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it towards cover.
Fuller ball, around middle and off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it towards mid off and takes a single.
FOUR! Poor delivery and punished! Angelo Mathews is not going to miss out on these! A shorter ball, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews pulls it towards the vacant fine leg for a boundary.
Fuller ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews drives it to the fielder at mid off.
Outside off, on a length. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.

FOUR! Easy pickings! A similar boundary to the previous one! Short once again, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews once again pulls it towards fine leg. The ball goes one bounce over the ropes for a boundary.
Fuller ball, loopy delivery, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it on the up towards cover.
Flatter ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out.
Marginally short now, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal works it away towards square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, width on offer this time. Angelo Mathews drives it uppishly away from his body towards cover-point for a single.
Fullish ball, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out towards mid-wicket.
Loopy delivery, around off, full in length. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it back to the bowler.
Shoriful Islam continues to bowl the short ball, around off this time. Angelo Mathews miscues his pull towards square leg for a single.
Better length this time! Outside off, good-length delivery. Dinesh Chandimal leaves it alone.
Length delivery, width on offer this time. Dinesh Chandimal cuts it towards the fielder at cover.
Fuller, tailing in, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it firmly towards the cover.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal ducks under it.
Length ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it off the back foot towards Mushfiqur Rahim at extra cover.
Flatter ball, darting it on the pads. Angelo Mathews flicks it towards square leg.
Shorter ball, quicker, flatter, on the pads. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards fine leg. Single taken!
Shakib Al Hasan continues to ball on the pads, shorter ball, flatter again. Dinesh Chandimal clips it past square leg for a brace.
Around middle and leg now, fuller in length. Dinesh Chandimal knocks it towards mid on off the front foot.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it down to long off for a single. He retains the strike.
Pitched up, around middle and off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it towards extra cover.
Tosses it up, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal leans to block this but the ball goes off the outer half of the bat towards square leg for a single.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around off. Angelo Mathews hangs back and knocks it towards long off for a single.
Loopy delivery, fuller in length, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Very full, around middle, loopy delivery. Angelo Mathews digs it back to the bowler.
Slightly quicker now, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews blocks it out towards mid-wicket.
Flighted delivery, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.
Fuller ball again, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal drives it down the ground for a single.
Loopy delivery, fuller in length, around middle. Angelo Mathews presses forward and defends it out towards the leg side.
Slower through the air, shorter ball, wide of off. Angelo Mathews cuts it and finds the fielder point.
Loopy delivery, fuller ball,a round middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Wide of off, fuller ball, slower through the air. Angelo Mathews lets that go through to the keeper.
Slower through the air, nicely tossed up, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal leans to drive, but the ball goes off the outside edge towards third man. Two taken!
Slightly short now, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal hangs back and blocks it out.
Tossed up ball, fuller in length, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal knocks it down to long on for a single.
Flatter and shorter, on middle. Angelo Mathews defends it off the back foot.
Short in length again, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards mid-wicket off the back foot.
Slower through the air, full, around middle and off. Angelo Mathews drives it towards long off for a single.
Shorter ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews defends it off the back foot.
Fuller now, attacking the stumps. Angelo Mathews presses forward and blocks it out.
Tad shorter, outside off. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards cover.
Quicker through th air, fuller in length, around off. Angelo Mathews defends it out off the front foot.
Quicker again, outside off. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Outside off, fuller in length. Angelo Mathews presses forward and blocks it out. That will be Stumps on Day 1!
Runs straightaway! A fuller ball, on the pads. Dinesh Chandimal flicks it towards deep square leg for a couple of runs. We are underway on Day 2!
Tad fuller, shaping away, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal leaves it alone.
Back of a length, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it towards the fielder at mid off.
Another shorter ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal punches it off the back foot but finds the fielder at cover.
On a length, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal lets that go through to the keeper.

Khaled Ahmed starts off with a fuller delivery, around off, at 129.2 clicks. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards on.

FOUR! Lovely shot for Angelo Mathews to begin with! He gets underway on Day 2 with a boundary! Another pitched up delivery, angling in, on the pads. Angelo Mathews uses his wrists and flicks it through square leg for a boundary.
On a length, around off, at 133.5 clicks. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Angling in on the pads, on a length, at 135.2 kph. Angelo Mathews clips it towards mid-wicket and takes a single.
On a length, outside off, at 133 clicks. Dinesh Chandimal shoulders his arms at it.
Length delivery, outside off, at 130.8 kph. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
A fuller ball from over the wicket, outside off, swinging away. Angelo Mathews does not fiddle with it.
An outswinger again, pitched up, wide of off. Angelo Mathews offers no shot.
Tighter line this time! On a length, around the fifth stump line, at around 128 clicks. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
A similar length again, maintains the line outside the off stump. Angelo Mathews lets that go through to the keeper.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Angelo Mathews shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller this time, around off. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards the right of the bowler. A maiden from Shoriful Islam! A much better over from him.

Tad fuller now, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it towards mid off.
