Pitched up, outside off, at 136.1. Dinesh Chandimal leans to drive but the ball goes off the inside edge towards fine leg for a single.
Beaten! Lovely delivery by Khaled Ahmed! A length ball, shaping away a tad, outside off. Angelo Mathews looks to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.

FOUR! Tad shorter, around middle, that did not bounce much. Angelo Mathews swivels and drags it with the inner half of his bat towards deep square leg for a boundary. Not the best follow-up delivery after the previous one.
A length delivery, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal dabs it towards point.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal punches it towards the fielder at mid on.
Fuller now, angling away, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal leans to drive but the ball goes off the inner half towards the right of the bowler.
Length ball, swinging away, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal leaves it alone.
Shoriful Islam drops it short now, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal ducks under it.
On a length, outside off, this one stays low as well. Dinesh Chandimal gets beaten as he tries to block this one. Another maiden from Shoriful Islam!
Shorter ball, spinning away, around middle and off. Angelo Mathews punches it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Much fuller now, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal presses forward and blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, slower through the air, full, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.
Tad quicker now, around middle, full in length. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out off his front foot.
Tosses it up, full in length, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal presses forward to block this but the ball goes off the inner half towards square leg. Single taken!
Pitched up delivery, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it firmly towards mid off. Mominul Haque slides to his left and makes a good stop. Single taken!
On a length, outside off. Angelo Mathews gets across and blocks it out off the back foot.
FOUR! Easy pickings! A shorter ball, around the leg pole. Angelo Mathews picks up the length, swivels, and pulls it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
Another short-pitched delivery, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews pulls it gently to fine leg and rotates the strike.
A fuller ball, outside off, shaping away. Dinesh Chandimal drives it to the fielder at cover.
Another full-length delivery from 'round the wicket this time, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal leaves it alone.
Flighted delivery, full, at around 77 clicks. Angelo Mathews blocks it out off the front foot.
Another loopy ball, around middle, tad quicker, at around 80 clicks. Angelo Mathews pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
Touch shorter, around off. Angelo Mathews chops it towards the fielder at point.
Tosses this one up, slower through the air, full in length, around off. Angelo Mathews drives it towards cover.
Spinning away a tad, outside off, marginally short. Angelo Mathews punches it towards cover for a single.
Loopy delivery, full, on middle. Dinesh Chandimal presents the full face of his bat and blocks it out solidly. Another tight over from Shakib Al Hasan.
A full toss to begin with, outside off. Angelo Mathews drives it towards cover. Mominul Haque dives to his right and makes a good stop. Saved a certain boundary there.
Tosses it up, full in length, on off. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
Outside off, very full, loopy ball. Angelo Mathews drives it to the fielder at short cover.
Flighted delivery, full in length, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Fuller ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews drives it to the fielder at short cover.
Tossed up ball, outside off, full again. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards cover. A maiden from Taijul Islam.
Spinning away, fuller ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out solidly.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Outside off, fuller in length. Dinesh Chandimal presses forward and drives it powerfully through cover for a boundary. That brings up the 100-run stand between these two!
Tossed up on middle. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out watchfully.
Too full on this occasion, loopy ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal squeezes it out towards the off side.
Shorter ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal cuts it towards point.
This one comes in with the angle, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal flicks it to mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, outside off, spinning away. Angelo Mathews drives it towards cover.
Outside off, tad quicker, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Tad shorter, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews works it away towards mid-wicket.
Slower through the air, full ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews pushes it to cover.
On middle, full in length. Angelo Mathews shows the full face of the bat and defends it out.
This one comes in, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews pushes it towards mid-wicket off the back foot.
Drifting in, around middle and leg, tad shorter. Dinesh Chandimal flicks it past mid-wicket and takes a single.
Fuller ball, darting it on the pads. Angelo Mathews presses forward and tucks it towards square leg. Litton Das runs to his left and will cut it out. Single taken!
Spinning away, fuller ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal drives it towards cover.
Full, on middle, loopy ball. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out watchfully.
Drifting it in on the pads, tad shorter. Dinesh Chandimal nudges it towards mid-wicket and takes a single.
Slower through the air, full, loopy ball, outside off. Angelo Mathews drives and find the fielder at cover.
Quicker ball, on middle, full in length. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.
Very full on this occasion, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal knocks it down to mid on and takes a single.
On middle, full in length, loopy ball. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
FOUR! Swept away! A fuller ball, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Quicker through the air, on middle, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Pitched up ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out watchfully.
On middle, defended.
On the stumps, kept out.
Floats it up on off, blocked.
Quick run! Would have been in though. On middle, this is worked to mid on. Chandimal goes for one. The fielder picks the ball up and has a shy at the bowler's end but misses.
Flighted delivery, fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews defends it out watchfully.
Slower through the air, full in length, around middle. Angelo Mathews defends it from within the crease.
Drifitn in, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out.
Shorter ball, quicker again, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal defedns it out off the back foot.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.
Quicker, around middle and off, full ball. Blocked out.
Outside off, fuller ball, loopy delivery. Dinesh Chandimal drives it past cover for a single.
Nicely tossed up, on middle, full in length. Angelo Mathews presents the full face of the bat and defends it out.
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal reverse-sweeps this past point for a single.
Fuller ball from over the wicket, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews tries to pad this away but he misses.
Full again, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
On the pads, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews clears his front foot and blocks it out.
Pitched up, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews tries to push this away behind the keeper, but he misses.
Another fuller ball, around the leg pole. Angelo Mathews clips it towards mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, spinning away a tad, around off. Dinesh Chandimal defends it towards cover.
On middle, fuller ball, tossed up as well. Dinesh Chandimal presses forward and defends it out.

Loopy delivery, around middle and leg, fuller ball. Dinesh Chandimal strokes it towards long off for a single. That will be fifty for Dinesh Chandimal. He brings his 21st Test half-century. It's been a solid knock so far.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around off. Angelo Mathews defends it out watchfully.
Another pitched up ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to the bowler.
This one drifts in, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews clips it towards mid on.
Shakib Al Hasan continues from over the wicket, and serves a fuller ball, down the leg side. Dinesh Chandimal sweeps it towards the fielder at square leg.
Fuller ball, on middle now. Dinesh Chandimal dances down the pitch and pushes it mid on for a single.
Tosses it up, full, around the leg pole. Angelo Mathews makes room and defends it out.
Around middle and off now, pitched up delivery. Angelo Mathews drives it gently towards the cover region for a single.
Down the leg side, fuller ball. Dinesh Chandimal looks to flick but he misses it out.
Around middle, fuller ball. Dinesh Chandimal nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews works it away to mid on for a single.
On middle, fuller ball. Dinesh Chandimal defends it out.

FOUR! Not from the middle of the bat and but that will go towards the boundary! Slower through the air, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal steps down the pitch and lofts it just over the man at mid on for a boundary. 300 up for Sri Lanka!
Outside off, fuller in length, quicker as well. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it towards point.

SIX! BANG! This is a much better shot from Dinesh Chandimal! Another fuller ball, tosses it up around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal shimmies down the pitch and heaves it over mid-wicket for a biggie.
Tad shorter, around middle and off. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out.
Nayeem Hasan begins with a shorter ball, wide of off. Angelo Mathews punches it off the back foot through cover for a brace.
Spinning in, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews defends it out off the back foot.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews hangs back and works it away towards mid-wicket for a single.
Pitches it up now, outside off, slower through the air. Dinesh Chandimal presses forward and blocks it on the off side.
Down the leg side now, fuller ball. Dinesh Chandimal gets down on his knee and sweeps it fine it towards fine leg. Two runs taken!
Marginally short now, around middle and leg. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it back to the bowler.
Extra bounce there! Tad shorter now, around off, spinning away. Angelo Mathews blocks it out off the back foot.
Much fuller on this occasion, around middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it to mid on for a single.
Fuller ball, tad quicker, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal has blocked this watchfully.
Shorter ball, around off. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it towards cover off the back foot.
Shakib Al Hasan spins this one in, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal blocks it out. A surprised look on Dinesh Chandimal's face after that delivery.
Shorter ball, outside off. Dinesh Chandimal pushes it towards extra cover for a single.
Tosses it up, fuller ball, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal steps down the track and works it away towards mid-wicket for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle, tossed up. Angelo Mathews nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Darting it on the pads, fuller ball. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards square leg for a single.
Shorter ball, quicker now, around off. Dinesh Chandimal hangs back and tries to block this but the ball goes off the outside edge towards short third for a single.
Fullish ball again, around middle. Angelo Mathews clips it to deep square leg for a single.
An off-break, fuller one, around middle. Dinesh Chandimal works it away to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, pitched up, around middle. Angelo Mathews leans forward and defends it out.
Another full ball, loopy delivery, around off. Angelo Mathews is solid in his front-foot defense.
Slower through the air, fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews defends it out off the front foot.
Outside off, full in length. Angelo Mathews presses forward and blocks it out.
Tad quicker, around middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it back to Shakib Al Hasan.
Fuller ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it off the front foot. Another maiden for Shakib Al Hasan.

OUT! LBW! Finally, Bangladesh have broken this stand. A much-needed wicket this for the hosts. They can breathe a sigh of relief for now. Nayeem Hasan grabs his third wicket and Sri Lanka have now lost half their side. A fuller ball, this one lands outside off and turns back in. Dinesh Chandimal gets down on his knee and tries to reverse-sweep this but he misses and gets hit on his pad. A huge appeal for LBW, and the umpire raises his finger. Dinesh Chandimal opts for a review. No bat involved, confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracking indicated three reds. Dinesh Chandimal does have to walk back after a solid knock.
Off the mark straightaway! Fuller ball, around the leg pole. Niroshan Dickwella gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards fine leg. Three taken!
Shortish ball, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews knocks it off the back foot towards mid-wicket for a single.
A fuller ball from over the wicket, around middle. Niroshan Dickwella blocks it out.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Double-strike for Bangladesh and for Nayeem Hasan! This is exactly what they needed. Niroshan Dickwella departs without doing much damage. Top stuff from Nayeem Hasan. He serves a shorter ball, quicker as well, this one comes in with the angle. Niroshan Dickwella stays back and tries to cut this away but he misses and the ball goes on to knock the off pole. Nayeem Hasan is now one away from a five-wicket haul! Ramesh Mendis walks out to bat next.
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle. Ramesh Mendis blocks it out solidly. A very successful over comes to an end.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around middle. Angelo Mathews defends it out.
Tad shorter, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it watchfully off the backfoot.
Loopy delivery, very full on middle. Angelo Mathews digs it out back to the bowler.
Another fuller ball, outside off, loopy one. Angelo Mathews presses forward and taps it towards cover for a single.
Tad shorter, around middle. Ramesh Mendis nudges it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around middle. Ramesh Mendis leans forward and defends it out.
Back of a length, spinning in, around middle. Angelo Mathews pushes it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Shorter ball, on the pads. Ramesh Mendis defends it out towards short leg.
Very full, loopy delivery. Ramesh Mendis flicks it past mid-wicket for a single. He gets off the mark!
Pitched up delivery from 'round the wicket, on the pads. Angelo Mathews nudges it towards square leg and rotates the strike.
Back to over the wicket for the right-hander, a shorter ball, around middle. Ramesh Mendis blocks it out.
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Ramesh Mendis defends it out off the back foot. That will be Lunch on Day 2!
On a length, Angelo Mathews plays it towards point and rotates the strike.

OUT! BOWLED! A perfect start for Bangladesh after the break! Shakib Al Hasan grabs his second wicket of the game and gets rid of Ramesh Mendis. He darts it around middle and leg, this one lands and straightens onto middle, and it stays low as well. Ramesh Mendis stays in his crease and tries to cut it but misses due to lack of bounce. The ball goes on to hit the stumps and Sri Lanka loses their seventh wicket immediately after the break. A much-needed one for Bangladesh.

OUT! LBW! Two in two for Shakib Al Hasan! Lasith Embuldeniya departs without scoring. Bangladesh on top early in the session! A fuller one, around the off pole, this comes in with the angle. Lasith Embuldeniya hangs back and tries to block it but misses and the ball hits his pads. A huge appeal and the finger goes up. Lasith Embuldeniya goes for the review. UltraEdge shows that no bat is involved and Ball Tracking indicates it is hitting the stumps and it's the umpire's call on impact. Lasith Embuldeniya has to walk away. Shakib Al Hasan is on a hat-trick now!
Fuller one outside off, Vishwa Fernando eases it towards covers and gets a single.
On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews hits it towards long on and gets a single.
On a good length and on off, Vishwa Fernando goes on the back foot and flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Flatter and on middle, this is pushed back to the bowler.
Tossed up on middle, defended.
On middle. Mathews works it through mid-wicket for one. Angelo Mathews brings up his 150! His partner now has three balls to play out.
Fernando gets off strike! Tossed up on off, Fernando plays it towards point and takes one.
TWO! Shorter and on middle, this is pushed towards long on for a couple.
Mathews retains strike! On middle, this is worked through mid-wicket for one.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller one again, Angelo Mathews defends it back towards the bowler.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews eases it towards silly mid on.
He sticks to bowling it fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
Fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews plays it towards silly mid on.
Goes fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews drives it towards mid off. He wanted to take a single and retain his strike but couldn't get it.
Fuller one on middle, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Vishwa Fernando defends it.
Fuller one on leg, Vishwa Fernando flicks it towards mid-wicket and gets Angelo Mathews back on strike.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews plays it towards mid on for one.
Goes full and on middle, this is defended.
Keeps his length and on middle, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid on region.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
On a length and on leg, Angelo Mathews opens up a bit and flicks it towards mid-wicket. Couple taken and Angelo Mathews keeps the strike.
Goes fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews goes on his backfoot and flicks it towards mid on for one.

On a length and on off, Vishwa Fernando tries to defend it but hits his pads first. Loud appeal by Shakib Al Hasan and the finger stays down. Bangladesh players go for the review. The replay confirms that it did hit the pad first. Ball Tracking shows that it was pitching outside off but the impact was outside as well. Bangladesh loses their final review. Vishwa Fernando takes a breath of relief.
Fuller one on middle, this is pushed towards mid-wicket.
On a length and on middle, this is defended.
Goes fuller again, this is blocked out.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews stays in his crease and blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, this is pushed towards covers for one.
Goes fuller again, Vishwa Fernando defends it solidly.
Keeps bowling it fuller and on middle, Vishwa Fernando does his job good and defends it.
Full toss on off, Angelo Mathews drives it towards covers.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it.
Fuller one again, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards backward square leg and takes a quick single. Leaves Vishwa Fernando with just two balls to defend.
Fuller one on middle, this is defended.
Goes fuller again, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
A dot. Goes fuller on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews uses his feet and hits it hard towards long on. He gets a single.
A full-length delivery outside off, Vishwa Fernando drives it towards covers for one.
Fuller one on off, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Fuller one outside off, Angelo Mathews cuts it towards point and gets a single.
Sticks to his length, this is defended.
On a full length outside off, Angelo Mathews leans forward and defends it.
Goes fuller again, Angelo Mathews stays in the crease and defends it.
Sticks to his length, Angelo Mathews cuts it towards point.
On off, this is blocked out.
Goes fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks this one out.
A maiden over. Sticks to his length, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid off. He wanted a single to keep the strike but couldn't take it.
Fuller one on middle, this is defended.

On a length and on middle, Vishwa Fernando tries to flick this away but he misses and it hits his pads. A loud appeal by Nayeem Hasan but the finger stays down. Bangladesh cannot refer this one, they have no reviews left!
On off, defended.
Goes fuller and on off, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Sticks to his length, Vishwa Fernando leans forward and defends it.
Goes fuller again, this is defended.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
Keeps bowling it on middle, Angelo Mathews defends it solidly.
Fuller one on leg, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid on for one.
Darts it on middle, this is blocked out.
Flatter one on middle, this is defended.
Goes fuller and on middle, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Fuller one on middle, Angelo Mathews gets on his knees and smashes it towards mid wicket. No run taken.
Goes fuller again, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid off and takes a single.
Darts it on middle, this is defended.
Fuller one on middle, this it pushed towards covers.
Sticks to his length, Vishwa Fernando defends it solidly.
On a length and on middle, Vishwa Fernando stays in his crease and blocks it out.
Darts it on leg, keeps it low as well. This is defended.
Flatter one on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Goes fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid off region. He wanted to take a single but couldn't.
Fuller one outside off, this is pushed away towards covers for one.
Fuller one outside off, Vishwa Fernando leaves it alone.
Goes fuller and on middle, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews opens up and flicks it towards mid-wicket. He takes a single.
On a full length and on middle, Vishwa Fernando defends it solidly.
Fuller one outside off, Vishwa Fernando eases it towards silly mid off.
Keeps it bowling fuller, this is blocked out.
Fuller one outside off spinning it away, Vishwa Fernando tries to defend it but gets beaten. He stays in his crease. This is good bowling from Nayeem Hasan.
On a length and on middle, Vishwa Fernando goes on his backfoot and defends it.
350 up for Lanka! On off, fuller, this is eased down to long off for one.
On middle, defended.
Tossed up on off, Vishwa Fernando pushes it to covers.
Floats it up on off, Vishwa Fernando pushes it to cover.
Down the leg side, Fernando looks to pull but misses.
On off, blocked.
On off, defended.
On off, this is pushed to cover.
On the fuller side, Mathews strokes it towards mid off for one.
Good length and on off, defended.
On the fuller side, this one tails back in. Blocked.
Another one on a length and around off, kept out.
On off, defended.
Flatter and on the stumps, kept out.
On off, kept out.
Angled into the pads, this is worked down to fine leg for one.
On the stumps, kept out.
Flatter and on middle, blocked.
Mathews is happy to take one on the first ball! On the pads, this is worked down to fine leg for one.
Good length and on off, this is pushed to cover.
Changes the angle, goes around the wicket and bangs it short. Fernando ducks under it.
Yet another short one on middle, Fernando yet again ducks under it. Two short balls, now time for a yorker?

FOUR! Off the outside edge! Fuller and outside off, Vishwa Fernando goes after it, this flies off the outside edge, past the gully fielder, and down to the third man fence. The ploy to go full almost worked but in the end, it is the batter who benefited from it.
Good length and on off, blocked.
Fuller and on middle, Mathews plays it back to the bowler.
On off, Mathews pushes it to covers.
Flatter and on the stumps, this is pushed to covers.
More runs! This lands on off and spins away. Mathews looks to push at it, this goes off the outside edge past the first slip fielder, down to third man and three is taken.
On middle, this is defended.
On middle, Fernando plays it back to the bowler.
Shorter one on middle, Angelo Mathews pulls it towards deep square leg for one.
On a length, slightly shorter angling it on off, Vishwa Fernando leaves it alone.
Shorter one on middle, Vishwa Fernando ducks under it. The ball goes towards the keeper.
Slower bouncer on middle, Vishwa Fernando ducks under it again.
Back of the length and on off, Vishwa Fernando eases it towards covers.
FOUR! Change of length, goes fuller this time, Vishwa Fernando times it perfectly and cuts it through third man region. The ball goes behind the ropes for a boundary.
Tossed up delivery one middle, this is eased towards mid-wicket for one.
Fuller one outside off, Vishwa Fernando plays it towards point.
FOUR! Goes slow this time, tossed up delivery on middle, Vishwa Fernando sweeps it to cow corner for a boundary.
On off, this is defended.
Fuller one on middle, Vishwa Fernando eases it towards square leg.
Tossed up delivery, Vishwa Fernando leans forward and defends it solidly.
Goes fuller outside off, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid off for one.
Shorter one on middle, Vishwa Fernando ducks it out.
Another shorter delivery, Vishwa Fernando leaves it alone.
Goes fuller this time, Vishwa Fernando defends it.
On a length, this is pushed away through covers.
On a length, slightly slower one this time, Vishwa Fernando flicks it towards mid-wicket.
Tossed up delivery on leg, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards short fine leg and rotates the strike.
On off, this is flicked towards mid wicket.

Dropped! Fuller one on off, Vishwa Fernando uses his feet and tries to loft it over mid on but doesn't get the power right. An easy catch dropped by Mushfiqur Rahim. An opportunity missed to break this partnership.
Fuller one on off, this is driven through covers for one.
On off, this is pushed towards covers.
Tossed up delivery, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out.
Back of the length, this is driven past covers. Good fielding there saving some runs for his team. Single taken.
Yorker one outside off, Vishwa Fernando tries to cut it but misses.
Shorter one on middle, Vishwa Fernando ducks it.

Shorter one on middle, Vishwa Fernando tries to duck it but the ball hits his helmet. Vishwa Fernando takes his helmet out and has a smile on his face. A relief for everyone to see he is okay. Slight halt in the game.
Sticks to blowing it shorter, Vishwa Fernando leaves it alone.
On a length, slightly shorter, Vishwa Fernando defends it solidly.
Quicker, fuller, down the leg side. Angelo Mathews leaves it alone.
Tosses this one up, full, around middle. Angelo Mathews presses forward and blocks it out.
Another loopy ball, pitches it up, on middle. Angelo Mathews leans forward and defends it out.
Fraction shorter, outside off. Angelo Mathews cuts it towards point. No run there.

Mix-up! But no harm done! A fuller ball, darting it on the pads. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards square leg. Asitha Fernando leaves his crease to sneak in a single but he is sent back mid-way. The fielder collects the ball and throws it towards the bowler. Shakib Al Hasan fails to grab it cleanly and Asitha Fernando returns back safely. A missed opportunity.
Flighted delivery, full again, around middle. Angelo Mathews blocks it out. Asitha Fernando will be on strike the next over!
On a length, outside off. Asitha Fernando pushes it out towards cover for a single.
Much fuller now, darting it on the pads. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards square leg for a brace.
Back of a length, around middle. Angelo Mathews pulls it gently towards deep square leg for a brace.
Good-length delivery, around middle and off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out solidly.
Another brace! Shoriful Islam drops it short now, outside off. Angelo Mathews pulls it towards deep mid-wicket. They came back for the second run!
Back of a length, around middle and leg. Angelo Mathews clips it towards mid-wicket. He wanted a single there, but he decides against it.
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Asitha Fernando presses forward and blocks it out.
Another loopy delivery, pitches it up once again, around middle. Asitha Fernando lunges forward and defends it out.
Pitched up, outside off. Blocked out.
Down the leg side, fuller ball. Asitha Fernando leaves it alone.
Flighted delivery, full, around off. Asitha Fernando blocks it out off the front foot.
Another tossed up ball, on middle. Asitha Fernando has defended this one.
On the pads, tad shorter. Angelo Mathews tucks it towards square leg for a single.

A huge shout for LBW, but the umpire says no! A fuller ball, coming in with the angle. Asitha Fernando looks to defend this but he miss and gets hit on his pads. The replay confirms that there was slight inside edge on that.
Loopy ball, full in length, around off. Asitha Fernando defends it out.
Outside off, fuller ball, loopy one. Asitha Fernando taps it to point.
Sharp turn now! A tossed up ball, spinning away, outside off. Asitha Fernando looks to have a poke at it but he misses.
Flighted delivery, full, around off. Asitha Fernando blocks it out. He survives the over!
Fuller one and on middle, this is defended.
Flatter one on middle spinning it towards leg, Angelo Mathews flicks it towards short fine leg.
On a length and on middle, Angelo Mathews blocks it out.
Shorter ball, around middle. Angelo Mathews knocks it to long on for a single.
Tossed up ball, fuller delivery, outside off. Asitha Fernando taps it towards point.
Tad quicker now, shroter. Asitha Fernando blocks it out off the back foot.
Loopy ball, fuller one, around off. Angelo Mathews blocks it out.

OUT! BOWLED! Tosses it up, spinning it in, Asitha Fernando tries to defend it but misses it completely. The ball hits the stumps. Also, fifer for Nayeem Hasan! An outstanding effort from the offie and his good start to his career continues. Asitha Fernando just played down the wrong line there. He probably thought the ball would turn a lot more than it did.
Fuller one on off, Vishwa Fernando blocks it out. A good over for Bangladesh getting a wicket. One more required to close the innings.

FOUR! THUMPED! Another one of those and Mathews inches closer to his double ton! Steps out, gets to the pitch of it and smashes it down the ground, past long on for a boundary.
Takes one, moves onto 197 and also keeps strike! Shorter and outside off, Mathews chops it towards cover for a quick run.
On middle, shorter, this is pushed to mid on.

Tossed up on off, Angelo works it to mid-wicket.
On middle, Mathews flicks it to mid-wicket.
Two and Mathews now moves to 199! He has one delivery in this over to get to a double ton! Shorter and outside off, Angelo guides it past point for a couple.

OUT! CAUGHT! Heartbreak for Angelo Mathews! He holes out one short of a double ton. End of an amazing innings from him, a few of the Bangladesh players come and give him a patt on his back too as he walks off but he is gutted. He can't believe he has not got that single run he needed to get to his second double century. He had just the one ball in this over to get to it and he tried to do so. The field was got in for him. He steps out, clever from Nayeem Hasan, he slows it up, drags his length back a little. Made Mathews reach for the ball. Angelo looks to whip it over the mid-wicket fielder but it goes more off the inner half and straight to Shakib at mid-wicket. He makes no mistake. Nayeem gets his sixth. That is the end of the Lankan innings. THEY END WITH 397!
Howout: c Shakib Al Hasan b Nayeem Hasan
