Slower through the air, full, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it back to the bowler.
Touch shorter now, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Around off, tad quicker, short ball. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it from within his crease.
A fuller ball, outside off. Litton Das leans and defends it out.
On a length, shaping away, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.
Pitches it up now, much straighter, on the pads. Litton Das flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
On the pads again, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim works it away towards mid-wicket. Single taken!
Change of length now! Kasun Rajitha drops it short, around off. Litton Das pulls it towards the deep mid-wicket. Only a single.
Width on offer, back-of-a-length delivery. Mushfiqur Rahim hangs back and cuts it towards points. The fielder makes a good stop there.
Slower through the air, very full, around middle and off. Litton Das lunges forward and blocks it solidly.
Another tossed up delivery, around off. Litton Das drives it down to long off and rotates the strike.
Floated delivery, very full, touch slower at around 79 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards the fielder at cover.
Another fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it towards point.
Very full, tosses it up, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim strokes it past the bowler towards long off for a single.
On middle, fuller ball. Litton Das blocks it out off the front foot.
An outswinger, outside off, on a length. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to slash this away but he misses.
Swinging away once again, wide of off, on a length, at around 133 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to cut this but he bails out at the end.
Angling in, on a length, around middle and leg, at 132.2 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it to square leg and runs across to the other end.
On a length, outside the off pole, at 133.5 clicks. Litton Das shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller now, around off, at around 134 kph. Litton Das presses forward and blocks it to cover.
Angles this one in, around middle and leg, on a good length. Litton Das taps it to square leg and takes a single. He retains the strike.
Slower through the air, full, spins away a tad, outside off. Litton Das leans and blocks it on the off side.
Drifting down the pads now, full in length. Litton Das tucks it fine towards fine leg. Three runs taken!  These are easy runs for Bangladesh!
Fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim offers no shot.
Tosses it up, pitches it up as well, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leans forward and defends it towards point.
Tad shorter now, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it to cover off the back foot.
Short again, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it from within his crease.
Full in length, outside off. Litton Das pushes it towards cover.
On a length, on the pads. Litton Das clips it towards deep square leg. Single taken!
Back of a length, tailing back in, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim taps it with soft hands towards square leg and takes an easy single.
FOUR! Lovely shot! Kasun Rajitha drops it short again, on the body. Litton Das swivels and pulls it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
Pitched up delivery, around off. Litton Das blocks it solidly off the front foot.
Down the leg side, fuller ball, at 133.4 kph. Litton Das misses his flick.
Marginally short, spinning away, outside of. Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it towards point off the back foot.
FOUR! Top shot! Good execution! A fuller ball, loopy one, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a boundary.
Tosses it up, full, on midde. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out solidly.
Another floated ball, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim shows the full face of the bat and defends it.
Very full, on middle, slower through the air. Mushfiqur Rahim works it away to the fielder at mid-wicket.
On middle, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it watchfully.
Back of a length, outside off. Litton Das punches it off the back foot square of the wicket on the off side. Single taken!
Angling in, on a length, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it towards deep square leg and takes a run.

No ball! Tad fuller, hint of away movement, around off. Litton Das looks to block this but the ball goes off the outside edge, one bounce towards gully. Kasun Rajitha has overstepped her and a no ball is called!
Good-length delivery, shaping away, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, tighter line now around the fifth stump. Litton Das lets that go through.
Touch fuller, around off. Litton Das prods and defends it watchfully.
Wide of off now, length delivery. Litton Das does not fiddle with it.
Fuller ball, loopy one, spins away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim prods forward and leaves it alone.
Yorker-length delivery, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it to the fielder at mid-wicket.
Outside off, turning away, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim offers no shot.
On the pads, fuller ball, slower through the air. Mushfiqur Rahim comes forward and defends it out.
Very full, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid on.
Another fuller ball, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to defend this but the ball goes off the outside edge wide of the slip fielder.
Asitha Fernando begins with a fuller ball, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.

Another pitched up delivery, around off. Litton Das presses forward and blocks it towards point. Litton Das leaves his crease for a single there but he is sent back at the end. A slight miscommunication but no harm done.
On a length, outside off. Litton Das dabs it wide of point and takes a quick single.
Angling in on the pads, a good-length delivery. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it towards deep square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, outside off. This has been driven nicely by Litton Das towards Dinesh Chandimal at cover.
Outside off, on a length. Litton Das watches it sail through to the keeper. Tidy first over from Asitha Fernando.
Fuller ball, on middle, tosses it up. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Close! An arm ball, outside off, shorter in length. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to cut this but the ball goes off the under edge just away from the stumps, and through the legs of the keeper.
Outside off, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Fuller, on the stumps. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Very full, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim drives it towards sweeper cover for a single.
Tosses it up, outside off, full in length. Litton Das steers it wide of the slip fielder. The ball goes towards third man and the batters take a single. Litton Das will retain the strike.
On a length, around middle and leg. Litton Das tucks it towards mid-wicket and takes a single.
Length delivery, outside off, at 137.8 clicks. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Another length ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller, outside off, at 136 kph. Mushfiqur Rahim lets that go through to the keeper.
Wide of off, length delivery. Left alone.
Full in length, around the fourth stump line. Mushfiqur Rahim drives it to the fielder at short cover.
Fuller ball, outside off, at around 80 clicks. Litton Das taps it to point off the back foot.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around off. Litton Das pushes it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Drifting down the leg side, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it to the fielder at deep square leg for a single.
Outside off, shorter ball. Litton Das pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
Drifting into middle and leg, shortish ball. Litton Das blocks it out.
Full in length, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.
Nipping back in, pitched up, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it over the bowler's head towards mid off.
Fuller ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim drives it towards cover.
Back of a length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim gets on his toes and blocks it towards point.
Wide of off, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim opens the face of the bat and drives it towards sweeper cover for a single. Mushfiqur Rahim is one away from 5000 Test runs!
Full in length, outside off. Litton Das drives it towards cover.
Shortish ball, outside off. Litton Das pushes it off the back foot through point for a single.
Tosses it up, full, spinning away, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.
Full, on the pads. Litton Das blocks it off the back foot.
Pitches it up, on middle. Litton Das presents the full face of the bat and defends it out.
Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Litton Das pushes it past cover off the back foot.
Tossed up, full, on middle. Litton Das lunges and defends it out.
Shorter, around middle and off. Litton Das blocks it off the back foot.
Back of a length, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it from within his crease towards point.

Shorter ball, down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim looks to leave this one but the ball goes off his gloves towards fine leg for a brace. Mushfiqur Rahim becomes the first player from Bangladesh to reach 5000 Test runs! What a player he has been! A proud moment for him and his entire nation. He joins an elite list as well.
Fuller ball, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim leans and blocks it out.
Fuller again, angling in around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim nudges it towards mid-wicket for a single.
Good-length delivery, outside off. Litton Das shuffles across and defends it out.
On a length, outside off. Litton Das leaves it alone.
Tossed up delivery, full in length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and sweeps it towards deep square leg for a brace.
Tad shorter, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it off the back foot.
Flighted delivery, full on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it solidly off the front foot.
Another fuller ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim prods forward and defends it out.
Loopy delivery, around middle, fuller ball. Mushfiqur Rahim dances down the pitch and looks to block this but he misses and gets hits on his pads.
Full, firing it on the stumps. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it off the back foot.
Very full, on middle. Litton Das works it away towards deep square leg for a single.
Shorter ball now, spinning in, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it towards deep square leg off the back foot for a single.
Another off-break, around middle, short ball. Litton Das flicks it from within his crease to deep square leg for a single.
Turning it in, around middle, short ball. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the back foot.
Short, an off-spinner, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Around middle and leg now, flatter ball. Mushfiqur Rahim tucks it towards fine leg for a single.
Tossed up delivery, full, on stumps. Mushfiqur Rahim knocks it down to long off for a single.
Too short on this occasion, spinning away, outside off. Litton Das punches it off the back foot towards deep cover for a brace.
Fuller ball, around middle, tosses it up. Litton Das presses forward and blocks it out.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around middle. Litton Das defends it off the back foot towards mid on.
Fuller ball, around middle. Litton Das defends it out
Tosses it up, full, around off. Litton Das presses forward and blocks it out.
Spinning in around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards short fine.
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it towards mid on for a single.
Tad shorter, turning in, around middle. Litton Das defends it out.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Litton Das presses forward and defends it out.
An off-break, around middle. Litton Das flicks it from within the crease towards mid-wicket.
Spinning in around middle and leg. Litton Das tucks it fine just away from leg slip.
Loopy ball, spinning away, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller again, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim prods forward and defends it out.
Much straighter now, outside off, shortish ball. Mushfiqur Rahim lets that go through to the keeper.
Fuller ball, tosses it up, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it away towards deep square leg for a single.
Outside off, shorter ball. Litton Das pushes it off the back foot towards cover for a single.
Spinning away, shorter ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it towards cover. Single taken!
Overpitched delivery, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim knocks it down to long on and rotates the strike.
Flighted delivery, full, on middle. Litton Das defends it solidly.
Tosses it up again, around off, full in length. Litton Das prods forward and defends it out.
Full in length, around middle. Litton Das flicks it off the front foot towards mid-wicket.
Firing down the leg side, shorter ball. Litton Das leaves it alone.

A huge appeal for LBW, but the umpire says no! A shorter ball, spinning in, on the pads. Litton Das looks to flick this off the back foot but the misses and gets hit on his pad. Dimuth Karunaratne opts for a review! No bat involved confirms UltraEdge. Ball Tracking indicates the ball was missing the stumps. It was sliding down leg. The on-field decision stands.
Tosses it up, full in length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Loopy ball again, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim gets down on his knee and looks to sweep this but the ball goes off the top edge towards fine leg. Three taken.
Outside off, spinning away, fuller ball. Left alone.
Flighted delivery, full, on middle. Litton Das prods and blocks it out.
This one comes in with the arm, around middle and leg. Litton Das defends it off the back foot.
Shorter ball, on the pads. Litton Das nudges it fine towards fine leg for a single.
Shorter ball, spinning in, around middle and leg. Litton Das pushes it off the back foot towards mid-wicket.
Back of a length, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller ball, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim leans to block this but he misses. The ball lobs up and lands away from the leg slip fielder.
Shorter ball, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards the leg side.
Attacking the stumps, short ball. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the back foot.
Fullish ball, outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it off the back foot towards third man for a single.
A fuller ball from over the wicket now, around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the front foot.
Loopy delivery, on the pads, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Loopy delivery, down the leg side, full in length. Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it towards square leg.
Shorter ball, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it off the back foot.
Loopy ball, full, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim prods and blocks it.
Pitches it up, around middle. Mushfiqur Rahim manages to get an inside edge on the pads.
Loopy ball, full, around off. Litton Das defends it out.
Spinning in around middle, shorter ball. Litton Das looks to tuck this away but he misses and gets hit high on his pads.
Very full, around middle and off. Litton Das knocks it down to long on for a single.
Shorter ball, turning in around middle and leg. Mushfiqur Rahim pulls it towards deep square leg. Single taken!
On middle, fuller ball. Litton Das prods and blocks it on the leg side.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Litton Das defends it off the front foot.
Very full from over the wicket, on middle. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out off the front foot.
Shorter ball, down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim defends it out.
Loopy delivery, down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim pads this away.
Very full, on middle, loopy one. Mushfiqur Rahim pushes it back to the bowler.
Full again, around off, tosses it up. Mushfiqur Rahim strokes it down to long off for a single.
Shorter ball, spinning away, around off. Litton Das pushes it through cover for a single. That will be Lunch on Day 4!

OUT! EDGED AND TAKEN! Sri Lanka have finally managed to break this partnership! What a start for Sri Lanka! Kasun Rajitha grabs his third wicket and Bangladesh are now 4 down! A shorter ball, wide of off. Litton Das stays in his crease and looks to cut this away, but only manages to get a slight outside edge back to the keeper. Niroshan Dickwella makes no mistake. Litton Das stands there in disbelief.
Howout: c Niroshan Dickwella b Kasun Rajitha

Commentary: OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Two in two for Kasun Rajitha! What an incredible turnaround this is! Kasun Rajitha gets another and he gets Sri Lanka back in the frame. A peach of a delivery! A length ball from 'round the wicket, nipping back in, around middle. Tamim Iqbal looks to drive this but he gets beaten. The ball sneaks in the gap between bat and pad and knocks the stumps over. Kasun Rajitha is on a hat-trick. Shakib Al Hasan walks out to face the hat-trick ball.
Angling in, very full, on middle. Shakib Al Hasan flicks it to mid-wicket. Shakib Al Hasan survives the hat-trick ball!
Outside off, fuller ball again. Shakib Al Hasan past point for a single.
Goes fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Sticks to bowling it wide outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim lets it go again.
On a good length and on middle, Shakib Al Hasan blocks it out.
Goes fuller, Shakib Al Hasan pushes the ball back towards Ramesh Mendis.
Another fuller one, this is eased towards the mid off region.
On a length and on off,  Shakib slaps it towards point and rotates the strike.
Sticks to his length, this is eased towards the mid-wicket region.
On a length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim with a solid defense.
Goes fuller on off, Shakib Al Hasan blocks it out.
FOUR! On a length and outisde off, Shakib Al Hasan tries to block it but gets a thick outside edge. The ball races past slip towards third man for a boundary. A much-needed one for Bangladesh!
Fuller and on middle, this is eased off towards mid off.
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and on middle, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
On a full length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and blocks it away.
Tossed up delivery on middle, this eased towards cover.
on a length outside off, Shakib Al Hasan cuts it towards backward point.
On leg, defended.
Fuller and on off, this is blocked out.
On a length and on middle, Shakib Al Hasan was in two minds but defends it in the end.

Goes fuller this time, on the pads. Shakib leans forward and flicks it towards short leg. The fielder there does an excellent job in taking the catch. A loud appeal from the players. The decision goes to the third umpire. Soft signal is given not out. The umpire upstairs goes with the soft signal as there is not enough evidence. It did look like it was brushing the ground though. Nevertheless a very tough decision. Shakib Al Hasan survives!
No ball! Fuller one on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it solidly. Kasun Rajitha has overstepped here and a no ball is called!
On a length and on off, this is eased towards covers for one.
Fuller and outside off, Shakib tries to cut it but misses.
Sticks to his length and line, Shakib Al Hasan defends it towards mid on.
Goes fuller and wide, this is knocked towards mid on.
Back of the length, slightly shorter, Shakib Al Hasan works it towards square leg and rotates the strike.
On a length outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Tossed up delivery on middle, Shakib Al Hasan blocks it towards mid off.
On a length outside off, Shakib Al Hasan goes on his back foot and pushes it past point. Gets a couple of runs.
Fuller one on leg, Shakib Al Hasan tries to defend it but misses. The ball hits his pads. A loud appeal from Ramesh Mendis but the finger stays down. That was probably sliding down leg.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed towards mid off for one.
Fuller and outside off, this is tapped towards deep point. They get a couple. Good running between the wickets.
On a length and on middle, this is pulled towards mid-wicket for one.
Fuller one outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Goes fuller again and on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, this is driven towards covers.

Fuller and on off, tailing back in. Mushfiqur Rahim tries to block it but he gets beaten on the inside edge. This is so close. The ball just aired past the off-stump as well. Mushfiqur Rahim gets lucky.
On off, this is eased towards point.
On a length and on middle, this is pushed back towards Kasun Rajitha.
Tossed up on middle, Shakib Al Hasan tries to sweep it but gets a top edge as it goes towards fine leg. The ball was in the air for some time but landed safely. A couple of runs taken.
On off, blocked.
FOUR! On a length and on middle, Shakib Al Hasan uses his feet and lofts it towrads for a boundary.
On middle, this is pushed towards covers for one.
Loopy one on middle, this is pushed towards short leg.
Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it towards mid on.
No ball! On a length and on middle, this is pushed towards the mid off region. Kasun Rajitha has overstepped and a no ball is called!
FOUR! On a length outside off, Shakib Al Hasan opens the face of the bat and drives it over cover. The ball races towards the fence for a boundary.
On middle, this is eased towards mid off for a single.
On middle, this is flicked towards backward square leg for one.
Fuller and outside off, Shakib Al Hasan drives it towards mid off. Good fielding from the fielder saving some runs for his team.
On leg, this is flicked towards backward square leg. Single taken!
On off, blocked.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards Dhananjaya de Silva.
On off, this is eased towards covers for one.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is blocked out.
Goes fuller, Mushfiqur Rahim uses his feet and defends it towards mid on.
On middle, this is blocked out.
On a length and on off, Mushfiqur Rahim sweeps it towards square leg and takes a single.
On a length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim cuts it towards point for one.
On a length and on leg, slightly shorter, Shakib Al Hasan leaves it alone.
Shorter one on middle, Shakib Al Hasan ducks under it.
Fuller and outside off, this is blocked out.
Shorter one on middle, Shakib Al Hasan looks to pull this but he gets an inside edge back on his helmet. He looks fine and is ready to go.
On a length and on leg, Shakib Al Hasan leaves it alone. The ball goes towards the keeper.
Tossed up on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards Dhananjaya de Silva.
Similar to last delivery, this is pushed back again towards Dhananjaya de Silva.
Fuller and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to sweep but gets a top edge. The ball was in the air for some time but just fell short of Dinesh Chandimal at deep square leg. Mushfiqur Rahim gets lucky!
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and on off, this is pushed towards mid off. A quick single taken.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Shorter one on middle, Shakib Al Hasan tries to scoop it over but the ball goes off his gloves into the glove of Niroshan Dickwella behind the stumps. The plan of Asitha Fernando luring Shakib Al Hasan with shorter deliveries has worked perfectly. Sri Lanka get their sixth wicket as Shakib Al Hasan walks away in disappointment.
Howout: c Niroshan Dickwella b Asitha Fernando

Commentary: Shorter one on middle again, this is quicker, Nayeem Hasan tries to flick it but misses. the ball hits his ribs. No runs taken.
Shorter one again, this one hits on the body of Nayeem Hasan again. Nayeem Hasan is asking for a chest guard as there is a slight halt in play.
Another shorter one on middle, Nayeem Hasan jumps a bit but ducks under it in the end. The ball goes towards the keeper.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
Shorter one again, darts in on middle, Nayeem Hasan fumbles a bit again as the ball hits his glove. Excellent wicket maiden over from Asitha Fernando.
Tossed up on middle, this is eased towards mid-wicket.
Fuller and on off, this is flicked towards mid-wicket for one.
Fuller and outside off, Nayeem Hasan tries to block it but misses.
On middle, defended.
This is similar to last one, Nayeem Hasan pushes it back towards Dhananjaya de Silva.
Fuller and on middle, this is eased towards short leg.
Shorter one on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it out.
Shorter one down leg, Mushfiqur Rahim leaves it alone.
Fuller and down the leg side, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick it but misses.
Shorter and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim ducks under it.
Fuller and on leg, this is flicked towards square leg for one.
Shorter one again, Nayeem Hasan jumps a bit and tries to defend. The ball hits his glove. He struggled a bit and needs some medical attention. Slight halt in play again.
Tossed up on leg, this is eased towards mid on.
Fuller one on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim puts his leg ahead of it and blocks it.
On leg, blocked.
Fuller one on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it behind. The ball goes towards fine leg and a couple of runs taken.
On middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim tries to play it but gets beaten. The ball hits his pads.
On a length, slightly shorter, this is blocked out.
Shorter one on middle, this is defended solidly.
On a length, slightly shorter, this is pulled towards fine leg for one.
Back of the length and on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim defends it solidly.
Shorter one on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it towards Asitha Fernando. Asitha Fernando stares at Mushfiqur Rahim and they exchange some words. Some mind games there from Asitha Fernando.
On off, this is defended.
Tossed up on middle, this is defended.
Similar to last delivery, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, Nayeem Hasan tries to block it but misses.
Fuller one on middle, thisi is pushed back towards Lasith Embuldeniya.
Fuller and on leg, Nayeem Hasan tries to flick it and just gets a tickle of his bat as the ball rolls towards short fine leg. A quick single taken.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended solidly.
Back of the length and on middle, this is pulled towards mid-wicket for one.
Shorter one on middle, Mushfiqur Rahim leans back a bit and leaves it towards the keeper.

FOUR! Hundred up for Mushfiqur Rahim. Back of the length and on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it towards fine leg for a boundary. What an innings from Mushfiqur Rahim. A loud cheer from the crowd. He removes his helmet and raises his bat. Take a bow, Mushfiqur Rahim.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
Back of the length and outside off, Mushfiqur Rahim gives a push towards point for one.
Shorter one on leg, this is flicked towards leg slip.
Tossed up delivery on leg, Mushfiqur Rahim lets it go.
on middle, this is defended.
Fuller one on leg, this is blocked out.
Fuller and outside off, this is driven towards covers for one.
Fuller and on off, this is defended solidly.
Fuller and on leg, Nayeem Hasan flicks it towards square leg. He wanted a single but Mushfiqur Rahim sends him back.
On middle, this is blocked out.
Similar to the last delivery, Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it again.
On middle, this is defended.
Fuller and on leg, this is flicked towards backward square leg for one.
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and on off, Nayeem Hasan tries to defend it but gets a slight outside edge. The ball goes towards backward point and a quick single taken before the tea break.
Starts up with a tossed up ball on middle, defended.
Flatter and on middle, Hasan pushes it to mid on.
Yet another one fired on middle, Nayeem gets his bat down in time and keeps it out.
Dickwella is showing a lot of excitment after every ball! Nayeem sees the funny side out of. On middle, blocked well.
And again, a huge roar from Dickwella after Nayeem plays the ball! On off, blocked out.
A maiden to begin after the break! Shorter and outside off, Hasan cuts it but to point.
Flatter and outside off, Rahim opens the face of the bat and guides it down towards third man for one. First run of the session.
On middle, Hasan works it to leg slip.
Really good energy shown by Dickwella from behind the stumps! On off, tossed up, blocked.
Yet another flighted, lands it around off, defended.
On off, shorter, this is pushed back to the bowler.
From around the wicket, this is fired on the pads, Hasan works it fine on the leg side and takes two.

OUT! TIMBER! Rahim can't believe he has been cleaned up! Sri Lanka gets the big fish immediately after the break. Just the kind of start they needed. End of a wonderful innings from Rahim. He though will be disappointed to have missed that one. This is tossed up, around leg. Rahim goes for the sweep, the ball turns towards the stumps. Rahim misses and the ball hits the leg pole. Lanka are into the lower-order now. Can they make quick work of the remaining wickets? Bangladesh's lead is 42.
No run.
Taijul is off the mark! On off, Taijul opens the face of the bat and guides it towards point for one.
On middle, Hasan defends it onto the ground.
Floats it up on off, Hasan pushes it to mid off.
Two to end! Shorter and outside off, Nayeem cuts it through point for two.
Angled into the pads, Taikul looks to flick but misses to get hit on the pads.
Angled into the pads again, this is worked through mid-wicket for one.
Down the leg side, Hasan leaves it alone.
Flatter and on middle, this is worked to mid-wicket.
Flighted ball on off, defended.
Around off, Hasan opens the face of the bat and guides it to point.
Tossed up on off, this is pushed to covers.
On off, loopy ball, it is kept out.
Yet another flighted delivery, Islam comes forward and defends.
On middle, Islam works it to mid-wicket.
Another one, nicely tossed up, around off, this one turns back in. Islam defends it onto the ground.

Edged but short! This is floated up on off, Islam comes forward to defend, the ball bounces extra after landing. It goes more off the shoulder but wide and short of the first slip fielder who dives to his left. A single.
ON middle, defended.
Tossed up on off, Islam keeps it out.
Outside off, Islam guides it to point.
On the stumps, kept out.
Fires it just outside off, Islam leaves it alone.
On middle, Ismal leans forward and blocks.
Angled into the pads, Hasan looks to flick but misses to get hit on the pads.
Fuller and on middle, Hasan pushes it to the left of mid on and takes one.
On off, blocked.
FOUR! Thumped down the ground! This is fuller and on middle, Islam slams it past the diving mid on fielder and into the fence. Lead is above fifty now.
BEATEN! This is floated up outside off, it goes on with the arm. Islam is beaten as he pokes at it.
A dot to end! On middle, defended.
Good start by Kasun! Length and around off, this one shapes away. Left alone well.
Angles it into the pads, Hasan looks to flick but misses. It hits the pad and rolls on the leg side.
Angled into middle, Hasan keeps it out.
BEATEN! That is a beauty! Length and on off, this lands and then moves away a long way. Hasan is beaten as he tries to defend.
On off, this time it is negotiated well.
On off, Hasan guides it to point.
Tossed up on middle, this is defended.
Fuller one mid middle, this is pushed back towards Dhananjaya de Silva.
On a length and on middle, Taijul Islam sweeps it towards square leg for one.
On middle, bloacked.
Fuller and on middle, Nayeem Hasan uses his feet and defends it.

OUT! CAUGHT! On a length and on middle, Nayeem Hasan leans forward and tries to defend it but the ball goes off his gloves due to some extra bounce. The ball goes towards short leg and an easy catch for Kusal Mendis who makes no mistake. Bangladesh lose their eighth wicket as Nayeem Hasan walks away.
Howout: c Kusal Mendis b Dhananjaya de Silva

Commentary: Fuller in length, nipping in, on middle, Taijul Islam tries to flick it but misses and hits his pads. A loud appeal for LBW and the finger goes up. Taijul Islam reviews it immediately. UltraEdge shows that there was no bat involved. Ball Tracking shows that it was pitching outside off but missing the stumps. Successful review from Bangladesh.
FOUR! Fuller and on leg, Taijul Islam flicks it past square leg, and the ball races towards the fence for a boundary. This is an excellent shot by Taijul Islam.
Outside off, Taijul Islam tries to slap it but misses. The ball goes towards the keeper.
This is really good bowling from Kasun Rajitha. Fuller and outside off, Taijul Islam tries to loft it but misses.
Fuller and outside off, this just goes past the bat of Taijul Islam.
Outside leg, this is left alone.
On middle, blocked.
Goes fuller and on off, this is pushed towards mid-wicket.
Dropped! An opportunity for Sri Lanka! Fuller and outside off, Shoriful Islam tries to flick it but gets an outside edge. There was a chance for Dickwella who drops it. Single taken.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed towards long on for one.
On middle, defended.
Fuller and on middle, this is blocked out.
On off, this is defended towards mid on.
Back of the length and on middle, this is pulled towards square leg for one.
Back of the length and on leg, Shoriful Islam tries to block it but misses. It hits his hips. He looks in a bit of trouble and needs some medical attention. A slight halt in play.
Shorter one around off, Shoriful Islam ducks under it.
Goes fuller and outside off, Shoriful Islam tries to drive it past covers but misses. The ball goes towards the keeper.
On a full length and on middle, this is blocked out.
Loopy one on off, Taijul Islam tries to loft it but doesn't get the power right. The ball just fell short of the fielder at mid on.
On middle, Taijul Islam uses hit feet and defends it.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and on off, this is punched towards covers.
On off, defended.
On off, Taijul Islam looks to drive this but the ball goes off the leading edge and falls short of the fielder backward point.
Fuller and on off, this is flicked towards mid-wicket. There was a chance for single but he refuses to take it.
Outside off, this is defended towards point.
Shorter one on off, Taijul Islam goes on his back foot and pulls it towards mid-wicket. The ball races past the fence for a boundary.
Shorter and on middle, Taijul Islam tries to flick it but misses.
Shorter and on off, Taijul Islam pulls it over square leg. The ball was in the air for quite some time but falls in no man's land.
Fuller and outside off, Shoriful Islam drives it towards deep point. A couple of runs taken. Seven runs of the over.
Shorter one on off, Taijul Islam leaves it alone towards the keeper.

OUT! CAUGHT! Asitha Fernando strikes again with a short-pitched delivery. Goes shorter and on middle, Taijul Islam tries to pull it but he gets a top edge and the ball goes towards fine leg. Chamika Karunaratne (sub), the man in control there makes no mistake. Nine down for Bangladesh now.
Howout: c sub Chamika Karunaratne b Asitha Fernando

Commentary: On middle, this is defended.
Shorter and outside off, Khaled Ahmed tries to cut it but misses.
Back of the length, Khaled Ahmed tries to flick it but misses.
On a length and on middle, Khaled Ahmed defends it back towards Asitha Fernando.
Back of the length outside off, Shoriful Islam tries to slap it but misses. Shoriful Islam struggles a bit with his wrist as he looks in pain. A slight halt in play.
Tossed up delivery on middle, this is blocked out.
Goes fuller and on middle, Oshada Fernando eases it towards point.
On a length and on middle, Oshada Fernando defends it towards silly mid off.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller again, Oshada Fernando defends it solidly.
Sticks to his length and on middle, Oshada Fernando blocks it out. A good maiden over by Nayeem Hasan.
Goes fuller outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.
FOUR! A fuller and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne opens the face of his bat and drives it through point for a boundary. Sri Lanka are underway!
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Goes full and outside off, this is defended towards mid off.
Sticks to his length, this is driven past mid off. Good chase by the fielder. A couple of runs taken.
FOUR! Fuller and on middle, Oshada Fernando uses his feet and lofts it over mid on. The ball goes behind the ropes for a one bounce boundary.
On middle, defended.
Fuller one on leg, Oshada Fernando fumbles a bit but lets it go in the end.
Loopy one on middle, this is defended.
Loopy one outside off, spinning in, Oshada Fernando tries to drive it but gets an inside edge back onto his pads. Oshada Fernando gets lucky there.
On middle, this is defended.
Tosses up on middle, this is pushed back towards Shakib Al Hasan.
Fuller and outside off, this is left alone.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended back towards the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, this is blocked towards short leg.
On middle, this is flicked towards square leg.
Sticks to his length, this is blocked out. A maiden over by Shakib Al Hasan.
Outside off, this is left alone.
Fuller and on off, this is driven past covers. A couple of runs taken.
Loopy one on leg, Oshada Fernando tries to flick it but misses. The ball hits his pads. A loud appeal from Nayeem Hasan but the umpire shows no interest.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed towards mid on for one.
On off, defended.
Goes fuller and on off, this is driven towards long on. A couple of runs taken.
Loopy one on middle, this is pushed back towards Shakib Al Hasan
on a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
outside off, this is defended towards short leg.
On off, blocked.
Sticks to bowling it on middle, Oshada Fernando defends its solidly.
On middle, this is eased towards mid off.
FOUR! A poor delivery, short and wide, Dimuth Karunaratne cuts it towards point for a boundary.
On middle, blocked.
Fuller and on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet and defends it solidly.

Fuller and on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne skips down the pitch and hits it straight back to the bowler. Nayeem takes a good low catch and celebrates. Dimuth Karunaratne though stays on the pitch. The decision goes towards the third umpire and the soft signal is out. The replays show that the ball just falls short of Nayeem Hasan. It brushes the ground before going into Nayeem Hasan's hands. NOT OUT says the third umpire!
On middle, blocked.
A loud shout by Nayeem Hasan again but the finger stays down. Fuller and on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to defend it but misses as it hits the pads. That probably seems to be sliding down leg.
On a length outside off, spinning it away, this is left alone.
On middle, blocked.
On a length and on off, this is eased towards silly point.
FOUR! Fuller and on middle, Oshada Fernando sweeps it towards fine leg for a boundary.
On a length and on middle, Oshada Fernando slap sweeps it towards short fine leg. A good chase by the fielder. A couple of runs taken.
Fuller and on middle, Oshada Fernando leans forward and defends it.
On a length and on middle, this is punched towards deep mid-wicket. Three runs taken.
On off, this is pushed towards square leg for one.
On middle, blocked.
On middle, Dimuth Karunaratne goes on his backfoot and punches it towards mid off.
Sticks to his length, this is blocked towards mid off.
Fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Tossed up on middle, this is eased towards silly point.
Similar to last delivery, this is defended.
On middle, blocked.
Goes fuller and on middle, This is pushed back towards Shakib Al Hasan.
Good length and on middle, this is defended.
FOUR! Fuller and on leg, Oshada Fernando sweeps it through backward square leg for a boundary.
Shorter ball, down the leg side. Dimuth Karunaratne looks to flick this but he misses.
Tosses it up, on middle, full in length. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward and blocks it out.
Shortish ball, outside off, spinning away. Dimuth Karunaratne hangs back and cuts it towards point for a single.
Serves a fuller ball from 'round the wicket, turning in, on middle. Oshada Fernando knocks it down the long on for a single.
Outside off, spinning away, fuller ball. Dimuth Karunaratne presses forward and defends it out watchfully.
Shorter ball, angling down the leg side. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it towards short fine leg.
Fuller ball, around middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne steps down the pitch and pushes it towards mid-wicket.
Shorter ball, angling down the leg side. Dimuth Karunaratne prods forward and looks to block this but he misses.
Shorter ball, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Another short ball, around middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it to the fielder at mid-wicket.

OUT! RUN OUT! Bangladesh have their first breakthrough! A mix-up in the middle and Oshada Fernando walks back to the hut. A shorter ball, turning in on middle. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it towards mid-wicket and leaves his crease. Oshada Fernando runs across as well, but he is sent back when he is halfway down the pitch. Taijul Islam collects the ball and scores a direct hit at the non-striker's end. Oshada Fernando puts in a dive but he fails to make his ground. OUT says the third umpire!
Another shorter ball, around middle and leg. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it towards the fielder at mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Tossed up on middle, this is blocked out.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended towards silly point.
On middle, this is pushed back towards Nayeem Hasan.
Fuller and on middle, this is defended solidly.
A maiden over! Tossed up on middle and off, Lasith Embuldeniya pushes it back towards Nayeem Hasan.
Loopy ball, full, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it wide of mid on for a single.
A fuller ball from over the wicket, slower through the air, on middle. Lasith Embuldeniya defends it out solidly.
Loopy one on middle, this is defended.
Similar to the last delivery, Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it again.
On middle, defended.
Fuller ball, outside off, loopy one as well. Lasith Embuldeniya prods forward and looks to block this but the ball goes off the outside edge away from the slip fielder. Single taken!
Tosses it up, full, outside off. Lasith Embuldeniya presses forward and defends it out.
Another tossed up ball, outside off, fuller ball. Lasith Embuldeniya once again lunges forward and defends it out.

Beaten! An absolute beauty by Nayeem Hasan! Tosses it up, full, this one lands around off and spins away. Lasith Embuldeniya leans forward and tries to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.
Drifting in around middle, shorter ball. Lasith Embuldeniya taps it towards square leg for a single.
Fuller ball, around middle and off. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out.
Back of a length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out off the back foot.
Quicker through the air, full, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya leans and tries to block this but the ball goes off the outside edge past the fielder at silly point.
Outside off, spinning in, shorter ball. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out.
Another shorter one, turning in, around middle, this one stays low as well. Lasith Embuldeniya does well to block this out.

NOT OUT! A fuller ball, spinning in, around off. Lasith Embuldeniya prods forward and tries to defend this but he misses. The ball goes on to hit the pads and lobs up towards silly point. A huge appeal and the umpire raises his finger. Lasith Embuldeniya reviews it immediately. UltraEdge confirms no bat involved. Ball Tracking indicates the impact was outside. The on-field decision has to overturned! Lasith Embuldeniya survies!
Shorter ball, outside off, this one keeps low as well. Lasith Embuldeniya looks to block this but he misses.
On middle, fuller ball. Lasith Embuldeniya blocks it out solidly.
Shorter ball, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Back of a length, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it from within his crease.
Shorter ball, around middle and off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
Tosses it up, full, around middle. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Angling on the pads, fuller ball. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out.
Beaten! A peach of a delivery! Shorter ball, spinning away, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne hangs back and looks to block this but he gets beaten on the outside edge.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Taijul Islam has his man! He did trouble him in his previous over but he gets him this time. That is a cracking delivery. Tosses it up, fuller one on off and turning it inside. Lasith Embuldeniya leans forward and tries to defend it but he misses it. The ball sneaks past his inside edge and goes on to hit the stumps. What a way to end the day. Sri Lanka are two down as Lasith Embuldeniya walks back in disappointment. That will be Stumps on Day 4!
Islam starts with a loopy one, this is eased towards covers. It is given as a no ball as the bowler oversteps.
Similar to the last delivery, this is defended towards the point region.
FOUR! First one of the day, On a length and outside off, this is driven past covers. The ball goes over the ropes for a boundary.
On off, blocked out.
FOUR! Short and on middle, this is pulled through mid on. The ball races past mid on as the fielder chases it but can only escort it to the boundary line.
FOUR! Short and on middle, this is pulled through mid on. The ball races past mid on as the fielder chases it but can only escort it to the boundary line.
Fuller and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to cut it but misses.
On a length and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it towards short mid-wicket. He gets a couple of runs.
On off, this is blocked.
Goes fuller and on off, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.
On a length and on off swinging it in, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to defend it but misses. This was close. The ball just aired past the stumps as it goes towards the keeper.
Outside off, this is left alone. Ohh its a no ball as the bowler oversteps. Ahmed needs to reload his final delivery.
On a length and on middle, this is pushed back towards Khaled Ahmed.
Fuller and on middle, this is blocked out. Ohh, no-ball again.
On off, blocked.
Sticks to bowling it on off, this is eased towards silly point.
Goes fuller and on off, this is eased towards covers. A quick single. This is good running between the wickets.
Flatter one outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet and defends it towards mid off.
Outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne puts his leg forwards and blocks it out.
On a length and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet and defends it.
FOUR! On a length, slightly shorter on leg, Kusal Mendis pulls it through deep square leg for a boundary.
FOUR! One more and this is just as similar to the last one. Goes shorter again, this is pulled again through deep square leg for a boundary. Poor delivery from Khaled Ahmed.
FOUR! Boundaries are raining here. Change of length bowling it outside off, this is driven past covers as the ball races past the fence. Kusal Mendis showing some good batting skills.
Shorter and wide outside off, Kusal Mendis moves to his backfoot and punches it towards covers. A couple of runs taken.
On a length and on middle, this is blocked out.
On a length and outside off, Kusal Mendis nudges it towards mid-wicket.
On middle, this is pushed towards long on for one.
FOUR! Kusal Mendis is on an aggressive mode here. On a length and outside off, Kusal Mendis uses his feet and lofts it ver mid on. The ball goes behind the ropes for a one bounce boundary.
A single now as this is worked down to long off.
Fuller, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne drives it through covers for a brace.
Another single as this is pushed down the ground.
Mendis stays back to this short delivery and punches it to cover but straight to the fielder. 9 runs come off it. Islam has been leaking runs in this morning session.
Goes fuller and outside off, this is defended.
Goes fuller and on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it towards mid-wicket and gets a brace.
On a length and on leg, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to defend it but fumbles a bit as it hits his pads. A loud appeal but the finger stays down.
On middle, this is blocked out solidly.
Goes fuller, this is defended towards silly point.
Goes fuller again, Dimuth Karunaratne leans back a bit and pushes it towards covers for one.
Fuller and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to cut it but misses. Gets lucky there.
On middle, this is defended towards mid on for a single.
Goes fuller and outside off, Kusal Mendis leans forward and eases it towards covers.
On off, this is blocked out solidly.
On a length and on middle, Kusal Mendis drives it towards covers for a single.
Goes fuller and wide outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne cuts it to point. Single taken.
Tosses up outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne lofts it towards mid off.
Fuller and outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne leaves it alone.
Goes fuller outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it towards covers for one.
FOUR! Back of the length, Kusal Mendis leans back and gets on his knees, flicks it over mid-wicket for a boundary.
SIX! Poor delivery from Nayeem Hasan. Back of the length and on middle, Kusal Mendis goes down on his knees and smashes it over mid-wicket for a maximum.
Goes fuller and outside off, Kusal Mendis plays it towards long on for one.
Floated and full, outside off. Mendis prods and blocks it to cover.
Full, on off. Mendis stays back and drives it to cover. The fielder there dives to his right to make a half-stop.
A dream delivery! Tosses up, full, around off. It turns away off the deck. Mendis tries to block it away but gets beaten on the outside edge.

FOUR! EDGY! Floated and full, on off. This one grips and turns away. Mendis gets on the front foot to defend it but only manages to get a thich outside edge. Luckily for him it goes between the slip fielder and the wicket-keeper for a boundary at third man.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Loopy ball, around off. Mendis remains solid in his defense.
Full, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne pushes it out to safety.
Fuller, on the pads. Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it to square leg.

Shakib Al Hasan asking the right questions here. It is floated and full, outside off. It turns in sharply and takes a fine inside edge. The ball lobs off the pads which takes it away from the keeper. A difficult chance to be honest.
Full and on off. Dimuth Karunaratne eases it to the off side.
Around off, blocked out.
A single then to end this probing over by Shakib Al Hasan. Full, on the pads, Dimuth Karunaratne clips it to mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, full and outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne comes down the track and eases it back to the bowler.
Dimuth Karunaratne dances down the track yet again to this full delivery. He works it to long on for a single. 100 up for Sri Lanka now.
Tossed up, around off. Kusal Mendis pushes it to mid off for a single.
Darted on the pads. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back and tucks it to mid-wicket.
Goes fuller, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet to smother the spin, as he defends it back to the bowler.
Touch short, outside off. Dimuth Karunaratne punches it through covers for a run.
Fuller, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne hits it towards long on for an easy single.
Tossed up, on off. Mendis defends it out watchfully.
Full, wide outside off. Kusal Mendis reaches out and defends it to cover.
On the pads, Mendis tucks it to square leg for one.
Full, on off. Dimuth Karunaratne defends it out on the front foot.
Around off, Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out to safety to see off this over. Just a couple of it. It has been a great start with the ball for Shakib Al Hasan so far in this morning session.
Full, on the stumps. Mendis prods and blocks it to cover.
Good running! Floated and full, drifts in from outside off and turns away a hint off the deck. Mendis uses the pace of the ball and guides it past backward point for a brace.
On off, defended out.
Goes full, on off. Mendis stays back to block it out.
Tossed up delivery outside off, Kusal Mendis blocks it towards silly point.
Only a couple off the over then. Brilliant over by Islam. Full and on off, defended out watchfully.
Fuller an outside off, Kusal Mendis blocks it towards silly point.
Goes on middle this time, this is pushed back towards Shakib Al Hasan.
Darts it on middle, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.
Outside off, Dimuth Karunaratne tries to punch it towards covers but misses.
Goes fuler this time, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feets and blocks it out solidly.
On a length and on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne nudges it towards short mid-wicket.
Tossed up on middle, this is blocked towards backward point.

OUT! BOWLED! This is excellent bowling from Taijul Islam. Slower on middle, gets just enough turn on off, Kusal Mendis tries to defend it but misses. The ball hits the off stump, as it turns away enough off the deck to get the first wicket of the day. Kusal Mendis looks back in surprise. Just the man Bangladesh wanted and they now have a chance to pressurize Sri Lanka.
On middle, quite slower, this is defended.
Sticks to his length and pace, this is defended out.
Fuller and outside off, Angelo Mathews tries to defend it buts gets a thick outside edge. Nothing to worry about for Angelo Mathews. This is clever bowling from Taijul Islam.
On middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller outside off, this is flicked towards mid on.
Another fuller one on off, this is flicked towards mid-wicket.
Similar to the last delivery, this is played towards the mid-wicket region.
On off, this is driven towards covers for one.
Goes fuller around the wicket, on off, this is eased towards silly point.
On a length and on off, Angelo Mathews pushes it towards mid on.
Tosses up on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet and blocks it to short leg.
On middle, this is blocked out.
On off, Dimuth Karunaratne defends it solidly.
Goes fuller and on off, Dimuth Karunaratne uses his feet and flicks it towards mid-wicket for a single.
On a full length and outside off, Angelo Mathews pushes it back towards Taijul Islam.
Similar to the last delivery, this is defended out.
Tossed up on middle, Dimuth Karunaratne flicks it to square leg for one.
On a length and wide outside off, Angelo Mathews opens up and eases it to point.
On middle, blocked out.
Goes fuller and on middle, this is pushed back towards the bowler.
Fuller and on middle, Angelo Mathews pushes it back towards the bowler.
Goes fuller again, Angelo Mathews eases it towards mid off.
Darted on the pads, Dimuth Karunaratne tucks it to square leg.
Floated and full, angled down leg. Dimuth Karunaratne stays back, tries to flick it away but misses.
On off, Dimuth Karunaratne blocks it out solidly.
A single now as Dimuth Karunaratne eases it to mid on.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! Angelo Mathews goes back on a 14-ball duck after an impressive 199 in the first innings. Taijul Islam grabs his third wicket but this time he gets rid of the big fish. It is full and on off. Angelo Mathews tries to break the shackles, but holes out instead. Mathews slaps it back to the bowler. Taijul Islam keeps his eyes on the ball and grabs the ball sharply. This is only the third time Angelo Mathews has been dismissed on a duck in Test cricket. Bangladesh with the advantage now.
